 v/custom/1380/opp_details/182492?slotid=1826828230311</a> <br><br>Descripti
 on: <span>Did you know that invasive plants are a huge threat to local wild
 life\, including migrating birds? Help out these creatures by volunteering 
 to remove invasive plants and restore habitat!</span><br><p><br>Registratio
 n for IMA workdays must be submitted by 3pm on the Friday prior to a weeken
 d workday and by 12pm on the day prior to a weekday workday.</p>
