DESCRIPTION:Join CCAN as we collect petition signatures to make polluters p
 ay for the climate damage they&#39\;ve caused in DC! <br><br><a href="https
 ://www.google.com/url?q=https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeMXj-ksN5
 ALh1OnEtnwKGe0hK6kTmKyZePBfOoGrEPIGPlVw/viewform?usp%3Ddialog&amp\;sa=D&amp
 \;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1756569158508128&amp\;usg=AOvVaw2tyzy6kzN8DRLHSo
 gAa3Gw" target="_blank">RSVP here</a>!<br><br><b>Where:</b> Bryant Street N
 E<br><b>When: </b>10am - 5pm<br><br>Climate change is here\, and DC residen
 ts are feeling the impact -through major storms\, flash floods\, and extrem
 e heat. Polluters need to be held accountable for the cost of these disaste
 rs\, which is why CCAN is launching our &quot\;Make Polluter Pay&quot\; cam
 paign! <br><br>To prove to Councilmembers that DC really cares about this\,
  we&#39\;ll need to demonstrate that their constituents care about making p
 olluters pay - that&#39\;s where YOU come in. Join us to collect petition s
 ignatures and build support in priority districts. As a special treat\, eac
 h volunteer will receive a FREE snack on CCAN! No tabling experience necess
 ary\, we&#39\;ll do a quick training on-site.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250825T155959Z
LOCATION:Bryant Street Northeast\, Bryant St NE\, Washington\, DC\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Tabling to Make Polluters Pay at DC State Fair
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
