DESCRIPTION:<p>Learn how your neighbors are lobbying for a clean energy fut
 ure. Over the past six weeks volunteers from our sister organization\, CCAN
  Action Fund\, have met with almost 15 Virginia elected officials! This is 
 critical work to set us up for success once those representatives travel to
  Richmond in January for the General Assembly.</p><p>But we’re not done yet
 ! On Tuesday December 17th we will hear from those volunteers and give you 
 a chance to plug into the movement\, while learning about upcoming climate 
 lobby days in January.</p><p>Can you join us on Tuesday?</p><h1><b><strong>
 <b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/76853/data/1">RSVP today
  for the Zoom info!</a></b></strong></b></h1>
LAST-MODIFIED:20241205T200958Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Virginia Action Member Meetup [Virtual Event]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
