DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://www.meetup.com/nova-new-leaf/events/312037344/
 ">See here for more details</a>\, or email Ting\, Northern VA Organizer\, a
 t ting@chesapeakeclimate.org<br><br>Next Sunday\, November 23\, we'll be he
 ading over to Annandale for our last Park Club of the year!<br><br><p>Come 
 join us for an Autumn Stroll! It will probably be a bit chilly so wear your
  coziest Autumn attire.</p>Park Club is where we as a community check out a
 nd explore different parks in Northern Virginia. Every park has something s
 pecial about it and people who use it regularly as a way to relax and recon
 nect with nature.
