 lay the impact that toxic air pollution would have on our health and climat
 e. Join us to make it clear – Dominion won’t get away with this!</p><p><b>R
 SVP now to join us in person in Chesterfield on Thursday\, November 16th.</
 b></p><p dir="ltr"><b>Location:</b> Springhill Suites Chester\, 12301 Redwa
 ter Creek Road\, Chester\, VA 23831</p><p><b>Time</b>: 5:00 PM community me
 eting\, 6:00 - 8:00 PM public briefing (come whenever you can!)<b><br></b><
 /p>
