DESCRIPTION:<p>Here’s the problem. Data centers use loads of electricity. I
 n Virginia right now we don’t require them to use renewable sources like wi
 nd and solar. In fact\, we subsidize them even if they run on dirty fossil 
 fuels. </p><p>Virginia regulators are currently studying this problem. Yet 
 at the same time\, local officials continue to approve dirty data centers. 
 </p><p>Join us on June 2nd to say: We need a pause on new data centers now!
 </p><p><strong><b>What</b></strong>: Rally to Stop Dirty Data Centers<br><s
 trong><b>When</b></strong>: Noon\, Sunday June 2\, 2024<br><strong><b>Where
 </b></strong>:  12098 Sunrise Valley Dr\, Reston\, VA 20191\, USA</p><h2><b
 ><strong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/68123/data/1">R
 SVP today!</a></b></strong></b></h2><br><b><strong><br></strong></b>
