 oadshow is an educational webinar that will help connect individuals\, orga
 nizations and municipalities to the landmark investments in clean energy\, 
 energy efficiency and community development initiatives. At this event folk
 s will have the opportunity to learn from experts about how to put these in
 vestments to use in their homes and communities. We will delve into the mos
 t relevant information so you can start benefiting from the IRA now.</span>
