DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Join us for our next</b></strong><br><strong><b>C
 CAN Maryland<br>Action Member Meetup </b></strong></p><p>This year\, Maryla
 nd has an opportunity to make history again in the fight against climate ch
 ange. Learn all about it — and how YOU can help — by joining the next CCAN 
 Maryland Action Member Meetup\, Wednesday August 23 at 7 PM. </p><p>In this
  month's meetup\, we’ll dive deep into our #1 legislative priority: making 
 polluters pay for the damages caused by the climate crisis. What does that 
 mean? How will we do that? Join the call and our legislative director\, Jam
 ie DeMarco\, will explain and let you know how you can get involved in gett
 ing landmark legislation passed. </p><p>We look forward to seeing you soon.
  <br><br><strong><b>Sign up now to join us Wednesday\, August 23 at 7:00 PM
 !</b></strong></p><p><strong><b>RSVP to get Zoom details! </b></strong><a h
 ref="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/55684/data/1">https://act.chesa
 peakeclimate.org/page/55684/data/1</a></p>
