 n learn the truth about the methane gas heating your home\, and what you ca
 n do to make a cleaner\, safer Washington D.C. Our first webinar on April 3
 0 will focus on how methane pollutes the atmosphere and contributes to the 
 climate crisis\, and what you can do about it! You can also join us on May 
 8 to learn about utility bills and May 22 to learn about the health impacts
  of methane. </p><br><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/820
 85/data/1">RSVP today!</a></b>
