DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Calling CCAN DC climate advocates and change-make
 rs!</b></strong></p><p>You're invited to our monthly DC Activists Meeting o
 n Thursday\, May 30 from 7:30-8:30 PM. We will meet on Zoom this month.</p>
 <p>Join us to meet other activists\, hear regular campaign updates\, learn 
 about upcoming actions\, and take an active role in planning our next steps
 .</p><p>Meetings will generally be held on the last Thursday of the month.<
