DESCRIPTION:<p>Electric vehicles are on the rise in Virginia. CCAN has been
  fighting for equitable mobility solutions for Virginians for years. But wh
 at’s next for clean transportation under an anti-climate governor like Youn
 gkin? And how can you get involved in your community?</p><p>Come to CCAN’s 
 virtual Action Member Meet Up on Tuesday September 24th to find out!</p><ul
 ><li>Get an overview of Virginia’s transportation emissions and policy solu
 tions from Victoria</li><li>Hear how volunteers like you in NoVA and Richmo
 nd are doing local work to support the mobility for all campaign. </li><li>
 Hear from our Hampton Roads organizer Leianis how expanding rural EV chargi
 ng access is a must for equity in Virginia.</li></ul><p>Then learn how you 
 can make a difference!</p><h1><b><strong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeake
 climate.org/page/73054/data/1">RSVP today for the Zoom info!</a></b></stron
 g></b></h1><br><b><strong><br></strong></b>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240913T205351Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:CCAN Virginia Action Member Meetup: Clean Transit for All [Virtual 
 event]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
