UID:7qs7vdg6pgn0mbsmgu8srcprj8@google.com
CREATED:20250828T172651Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>The Public Service Commission is hosting a final hearing on 
 District (un)SAFE\, Washington Gas’s request for a blank check to spend mil
 lions on methane gas infrastructure with no proof it will stop super-emitte
 r gas leaks. We’re not fooled: this is yet another version of Project Pipes
 \, and it will not make anyone in the District safer. The Commission has th
 e power to fix this over-budget\, ineffective program once and for all. And
  if they won’t do it\, then we’re calling on the D.C. Council to step in to
  protect us from even higher utility bills. </p><p>The Commission heard fro
 m you in nearly 700 public comments and dozens of testimonies at community 
 hearings. And now\, it’s almost decision time. So let’s make sure they don’
 t forget our message: no more money for Washington Gas’s failing cash grab!
  </p><p>Rally with us outside the PSC at 8:15am before the hearing kicks of
 f. Then\, we’re heading two blocks to the Wilson Building to make the D.C. 
 Council hears from us too. It’s time to STOP PROJECT PIPES! </p><p><b><b>WH
 AT: </b></b>Rally and Hearing to Stop Project Pipes / District (un)SAFE<br>
 <strong><b>WHEN: </b></strong>Tuesday\, November 18th\, 8:15 AM rally\, 9:0
 0 AM hearing<br><b><b>WHERE: </b></b>DC Public Service Commission\, 1325 G 
 St NW #800\, Washington\, DC 20005</p><h3><strong><b><a href="https://act.c
 hesapeakeclimate.org/page/87618/data/1" target="_blank">RSVP Today!</a></b>
 </strong></h3><br><strong><br></strong>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250924T134127Z
LOCATION:Public Service Commission of the District of Columbia\, 1325 G St 
 NW #800\, Washington\, DC 20005\, USA
SEQUENCE:3
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:DC Stop Project Pipes Rally
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
