DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Virginia's referendum on Congressional redistrict
 ing is a generational vote – one that will likely decide control of Congres
 s next year. No one can afford to not vote. </b></strong></p><p>Polls have 
 this referendum in a dead heat\, with early voting currently underway and t
 he final day to vote being Tuesday\, April 21st. CCAN Action Fund is hostin
 g our first redistricting phonebank on <strong><b>Thursday\, April 2nd from
  6:00 - 7:00 PM ET.</b></strong> We will be calling other CCAN members acro
 ss Virginia and make sure they’re voting\, see if they can activate their f
 riends and family\, and ask them to volunteer as well. Don’t miss this chan
 ce to get involved with the referendum that could determine control of Cong
 ress. </p><p><strong><b>WHEN</b></strong>: Thursday\, April 2nd from 6:00 -
  7:00 PM ET.</p><p><strong><b>WHERE</b></strong>: Your computer! Sign up fo
 r the Zoom link. </p><p><strong><b><a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/
 page/96034/data/1">RSVP today!</a></b></strong></p><p><strong><br></strong>
 </p>
