DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Join our testimony writing party!</b></strong></p
 ><p>On January 31st\, the DC Council is holding the oversight hearing for t
 he DC Public Service Commission. This is the agency that regulates DC’s uti
 lity companies and they have the power to reject Project Pipes. The public 
 is invited to testify before the Council\, and so we will gather virtually 
 on the evening of January 29th to support one another in writing strong and
  meaningful testimonies.</p><p>If you haven’t yet signed up to testify\, <a
  href="https://lims.dccouncil.gov/Hearings/register-to-testify/256">you can
  do so here.</a></p><p><strong><b>Then please register below to receive the
  zoom link for the testimony writing party.</b></strong></p><p><strong><b><
 a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/62509/data/1">RSVP today!</a></
 b></strong></p>
