DESCRIPTION:Join CCAN as we collect petition signatures to make polluters p
 ay for the climate damage they&#39\;ve caused in DC!<b> <a href="https://ww
 w.google.com/url?q=https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/86067/data/1&amp\
 ;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1754161031643034&amp\;usg=AOvVaw2rYNQC_
 3XkvsItxDvuXk0c" target="_blank">RSVP here.</a></b><br><br><b>Where:</b> Pe
 tworth Community Market\; 9th and Upshur St. NW <br><b>When: </b>9am - 1pm 
 <br><br>Climate change is here\, and DC residents are feeling the impact -t
 hrough major storms\, flash floods\, and extreme heat. Polluters need to be
  held accountable for the cost of these disasters\, which is why CCAN is la
 unching our &quot\;Make Polluter Pay&quot\; campaign! <br><br>To prove to C
 ouncilmembers that DC really cares about this\, we&#39\;ll need to demonstr
 ate that their constituents care about making polluters pay - that&#39\;s w
 here YOU come in. Join us to collect petition signatures and build support 
 in priority districts. As a special treat\, each volunteer will receive a F
 REE snack on CCAN! No tabling experience necessary\, we&#39\;ll do a quick 
 training on-site.<br><br>Please reach out to Ayla (<a href="mailto:aylaf@ch
 esapeakeclimate.org" target="_blank">aylaf@chesapeakeclimate.org</a>) with 
 any questions or accommodations.
