DESCRIPTION:<p>CCAN Action Fund and the Sierra Club are co-hosting the Gras
 sroots Climate Lobby Day in mid-February. <strong><b>But before we travel t
 o Richmond\, we want to make sure volunteers like you are prepared!</b></st
 rong></p><p>Join us on Tuesday\, February 10 at 7:00 PM for a virtual call.
  We will go through a refresher on how to lobby\, share our priority bills 
 and give an update on the General Assembly. Then we will make space to answ
 er logistical questions about the Climate Lobby Day one week later.</p><p>J
 oin us on the 10th to get prepared for Grassroots Climate Lobby Day!</p><p>
