 on Sunday June 22nd in Chesapeake\, VA (900 City Park Dr\, Chesapeake\, Vir
 ginia 23320) from 10am-5pm. When you RSVP make sure to check the box for th
 e shift(s) you can attend! As a special treat\, each volunteer will receive
