DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Calling all Hampton Roads climate advocates and c
 hange-makers!</b></strong></p><p>Our next 757 Climate Action Team meeting i
 s scheduled for <strong><b>Sunday February 15th\, from 1:00 - 3:00 PM in do
 wntown Norfolk</b></strong>. Expect icebreakers\, snacks\, and real discuss
 ions about how to make a difference in Hampton Roads climate advocacy. </p>
 <p>Our next meeting will primarily be focused on the following:</p><ul><li>
 CCAN's legislative update! Come together with other climate activists to di
 scuss our progress in getting climate legislation passed in Virginia :) </l
 i><li>Learn more about CCAN’s legislative priorities &amp\; campaigns</li><
 li>Meet other climate activists in the area!</li><li>Help plan for our Lobb
 y day on February 17th!</li><li>Snacks and treats!!</li></ul><p>This meetin
 g will be <strong><b>hybrid </b></strong>to accommodate members who can't m
 ake it in-person\, but want to join the meeting online. <em>Snacks and refr
 eshments will be provided for those who attend in person!</em></p><p>Don’t 
 miss out—secure your spot today and be a part of something transformative!<
 /p><h1><b><strong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/93926/
 data/1">RSVP today for the location and virtual link!</a></b></strong></b><
 /h1><br><b><strong><br></strong></b>
