CREATED:20250825T160026Z
DESCRIPTION:Join CCAN as we collect petition signatures to make polluters p
 ay for the climate damage they&#39\;ve caused in DC! <br><br><a href="https
 ://www.google.com/url?q=https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeMXj-ksN5
 ALh1OnEtnwKGe0hK6kTmKyZePBfOoGrEPIGPlVw/viewform?usp%3Ddialog&amp\;sa=D&amp
 \;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1756569478916908&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0tWFcuwb-kzYfLD_
 DSrlTN" target="_blank">RSVP here</a>!<br><br><b>Where:</b> Uptwon Farmer&#
 39\;s Market: 5500 Colorado Ave NW<br><b>When: </b>9am - 1pm<br><br>Climate
  change is here\, and DC residents are feeling the impact -through major st
 orms\, flash floods\, and extreme heat. Polluters need to be held accountab
 le for the cost of these disasters\, which is why CCAN is launching our &qu
 ot\;Make Polluter Pay&quot\; campaign! <br><br>To prove to Councilmembers t
 hat DC really cares about this\, we&#39\;ll need to demonstrate that their 
 constituents care about making polluters pay - that&#39\;s where YOU come i
 n. Join us to collect petition signatures and build support in priority dis
 tricts. As a special treat\, each volunteer will receive a FREE snack on CC
 AN! No tabling experience necessary\, we&#39\;ll do a quick training on-sit
 e.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250825T160027Z
LOCATION:5500 Colorado Ave NW
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Tabling to Make Polluters Pay at Uptown Farmer's Market 
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
