  or local lawmaker about why they should take climate action\, do you know 
 what would you say? </p><p>No problem.</p><p>That’s where CCAN Action Fund’
 s "How to Lobby" Training comes in. Join us on Thursday October 23rd from 6
 :30 - 8:00 PM. During the training\, you will:</p><ul><li>Learn how you can
  make your voice heard </li><li> Learn our guidelines for having effective 
  lobby meetings.</li><li> Meet with the lobby team from your legislative di
 stricts and prepare for in-district meetings to be conducted this fall. </l
 i></ul><p><strong><b>WHAT: </b></strong><strong><b>How To Talk To MD Legisl
 ators About Climate Action - Free Training!</b></strong><br><strong><b>WHEN
 :</b></strong> Thursday October 23rd from 6:30 - 8:00 PM ET<br><strong><b>W
 HERE:</b></strong> Your computer! Zoom info provided upon RSVP.</p><h3><a h
 ref="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/89238/data/1">RSVP today!</a></h3>
