 ence in the Richmond area\, our action team is the right place for you. </p
 ><p dir="ltr">Our next meeting is scheduled for <b>Wednesday\, Feb 19th\, f
 rom 7pm-8pm in downtown Richmond</b>. Expect real discussions about how to 
 make a difference in Richmond climate advocacy. </p><p dir="ltr">On Wednesd
 ay you can learn more about our existing events and join a discussion on ou
 r priority local campaign.</p><p dir="ltr">This meeting will be <b>hybrid</
 b> to accommodate members who can't make it in-person\, but want to join th
 e meeting online. <i>Snacks and refreshments will be provided for those who
  attend in person!</i></p><p dir="ltr">Don’t miss out—secure your spot toda
 y and be a part of something transformative!</p><h1 dir="ltr"><b><a href="h
 ttps://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/79110/data/1">RSVP today for the loca
