DESCRIPTION:<p><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/61434/dat
 a/1">Join us for pizzas and posters!</a></b></p><p>The Virginia Reliability
  Project - what we're calling the "Virginia Ripoff Project" - is a gas pipe
 line replacement proposal that would do irreversible harm to our drinking w
 ater\, ecosystems\, and communities. We need to stop it!</p><p>Join our pos
 ter-making night to stimulate your creative muscles and create eye-catching
  posters. With an in-person demonstration coming up\, this is a great way t
 o create compelling imagery and tell your story. And eat free pizza too!</p
 ><p><b>WHERE: </b><b>RSVP to receive address</b></p><p><b>WHEN: 6:30-9:00 P
 M (or however long works for you)</b></p><p><b><a href="https://act.chesape
 akeclimate.org/page/61434/data/1">RSVP today!</a></b></p>
