DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Chesapeake Climate Action Network\,</b></strong> 
 Appalachian Voices\, Unitarian Universalist Church – Roanoke\, and Baseline
  Solar invite you to come to our upcoming #ElectrifyEverything Roadshow in 
 Roanoke! At this event\, you’ll learn about the Inflation Reduction Act\, a
 nd how you can use it to install sustainable\, electric technologies in you
 r home right now (e.g.\, like solar panels\, a new stove\, or HVAC) with go
 vernment support.</p><p><strong><b>WHERE</b></strong>: Join us at the Roano
 ke Public Library - Auditorium  (706 S Jefferson St.\, Roanoke\, VA 24016) 
 <br><strong><b>WHEN</b></strong>: Thursday\, July 27th from 6:00pm - 7:30 P
 M ET</p><p>Here's the schedule: </p><ul><li>6:00-6:20 PM: FREE food! </li><
 li>6:20-6:30 PM: Opening Remarks</li><li>6:30-7:15 PM: ElectrifyEverything 
 Roadshow Workshop<ul><li>What is the Inflation Reduction Act (IRA)?</li><li
 >IRA Tax Credits and Rebates </li><li>IRA for Tax-Exempt Entities  </li><li
 >Electric Vehicles</li><li>Home Electrification Improvements </li><li>How d
 o I advocate for state and local action?</li></ul></li><li>7:15-7:30 PM: co
 nclusion and next steps</li></ul><h2><b><strong><b><a href="https://act.che
 sapeakeclimate.org/page/54587/data/1">RSVP today!</a></b></strong></b></h2>
 <br><b><strong><br></strong></b>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230717T183832Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:#ElectrifyEverything Roadshow in Roanoke [CCAN Event]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
