 oin us for our next CCAN Maryland Action Member Meetup </b></a><p><br></p><
 p>Get the latest updates on our Maryland climate campaigns. Hear from CCAN 
 staff and volunteer leaders about the amazing work we are doing on the grou
 nd to build community and support each other while organizing to advance cl
 imate justice in our own communities. <br></p><p>We'll hear about our effor
 ts to pass a bill to Make Polluters Pay for climate solutions\, then our st
 rategy to elect key climate champions this year\, including Kamala Harris!<
 /p><p><b><a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/71415/data/1">RSVP to
 day!</a></b></p><p><br></p>
