CREATED:20250623T190941Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><b>Calling all Central Virginia climate advocates and change
 -makers! </b></p><p>Join us on June 25th  from 7:00–8:00 PM for RCCA’s June
  Meeting!</p><p>This month’s meeting will be packed with energy\, purpose\,
  and action. We will spotlight the urgent fight against Dominion’s proposed
  gas plant in Chesterfield\, including a special preview of the powerful No
  Gas Plant documentary presented by guest speaker Will Selden. We will also
  report back on major advocacy efforts - from our lobby meeting with Senato
 r Deeds to community victories at the Big Gay Market and a new Water Justic
 e Initiative led by Eliezer Ferrel</p><p>This meeting will be <b>hybrid</b>
  to accommodate members who can't make it in-person\, but want to join the 
 meeting online. Dinner will be provided for in-person attendeees. Don’t mis
 s out!</p><h1><b><strong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page
 /84824/data/1">RSVP today for the location and virtual link!</a></b></stron
 g></b></h1>
