 ucture are OVER!</p><p><strong><b>WHAT: </b></strong>Rally to stop Dominion
 's new methane gas plant proposal<br><strong><b>WHEN: </b></strong>Tuesday 
 June 27\, 4:00PM<br><strong><b>WHERE: </b></strong>Outside Bellwood Element
 ary School (9536 Dawnshire Road\, North Chesterfield\, VA 23237)</p><p><b><
 a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/53863/data/1">RSVP today!</a
 ></b></p><p><br></p>
