 slation to expand clean energy and end fossil fuels. </p><p><strong><b>WHAT
 : </b></strong>CCAN Action Fund How to Lobby Training<br><strong><b>WHEN:</
 b></strong> Thursday\, January 25th\, 7:00-8:30 PM ET<br><strong><b>WHERE:<
 /b></strong> From the comfort of your own home. RSVP for the Zoom link!</p>
