 utm_source=Trainings&amp\;utm_medium=Email&amp\;utm_campaign=Unlocking+Your
 +Impact+Series</a><br><br>Description: <span>Families across the country ar
 e feeling the consequences of our national housing shortage and affordabili
 ty crisis. Although access to affordable housing is a national challenge\, 
 most immediate solutions happen in our own communities.</span><br><p>Join u
 s for our Unlocking Your Impact: How to Show Up In Your Community training 
 to learn how YIMBYs are leading the charge for more homes in their local co
 mmunities. You’ll learn about the role of local governments in our housing 
 system and how to get involved in community politics—even with no experienc
 e—to fight for more homes</p><br>This event will be offered virtually via Z
 oom. Live closed captioning will be available\, and a recording of the even
 t will be sent to people who register afterward.
