  in Silver Spring!</b></strong></p><p>Come to Silver Spring at 1:00pm on Su
 nday\, February 15th to make your voice heard about local climate and clean
  energy issues! Montgomery County’s state and local elected officials are w
 orking to pass critical policies about data centers\, solar panels for rent
 ers\, and utility bills\, and they want to hear from you. </p><p>CCAN Actio
 n Fund is hosting a testimony writing party to prepare our community for Mo
 ntgomery County’s data center policy hearing and for the Affordable Solar A
 ct in Annapolis. Learn more about the issues\, meet other advocates in the 
 area\, and enjoy some yummy food. All are welcome! </p><p><br><b>WHAT: </b>
 Montgomery County Testimony Writing Party  <br><b>WHEN:</b> Sunday\, Februa
 ry 15\, 1:00-2:30 PM ET<br><b>WHERE:</b> Downtown Silver Spring - address w
 ill be sent to RSVPs</p><ul><li>We’ll provide you everything you need to kn
 ow. All you need to do is show up!</li><li>Please do RSVP to receive the ad
 dress -- and also so we know how much snacks and drinks to have on hand.<br
 > </li></ul><h3><strong><b><a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/937
 73/data/1">RSVP today for Event location!</a></b></strong></h3>
