 ata/1">Happy hour for a methane-free DC!</a></strong><br></p><p>Project Pip
 es\, Washington Gas’ accelerated pipe replacement plan\, will lock D.C. res
 idents into an energy system that contributes to climate change and threate
 ns community health\, saddling taxpayers with the burden of paying for it. 
 The Stop Project Pipes campaign is doing everything we can to stop it! <br>
 </p><p>To support\, join us on February 22nd at the Stop Project Pipes Happ
 y Hour! Hear updates on the campaign\, learn about upcoming opportunities t
 o get involved as an individual or organization\, and build community with 
 like-minded volunteers and community organizations. <br></p><p><em><strong>
 Free vegetarian appetizers and one free drink ticket will be provided to al
 l event attendees.</strong></em><br></p><p> WHAT: Stop Project Pipes Happy 
 Hour <br>WHERE: Madhatter – 1319 Connecticut Ave NW\, Washington\, <br>D.C.
  WHEN: Thursday\, February 22nd\, 6:00 – 8:00 pm <br>WHO: All are welcome!<
 br></p><p><strong><a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/62946/data/1
 ">RSVP today!</a></strong></p>
