DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Chesapeake Climate Action Network\, Appalachian V
 oices\, The City of Harrisonburg\, Climate Action Alliance of the Valley\, 
 Community Housing Partners\, and Virginia Clean Cities</b></strong> invite 
 you to come to our upcoming #ElectrifyEverything Roadshow in Harrisonburg! 
 At this event\, you’ll learn about the Inflation Reduction Act\, and how yo
 u can use it to install sustainable\, electric technologies in your home ri
 ght now (e.g.\, like solar panels\, a new stove\, or HVAC) with government 
 support.</p><p><strong><b>WHERE</b></strong>: Join us at the Lucy F. Simms 
 Continuing Education Center (620 Simms Ave.\, Harrisonburg\, VA 22802)<br><
 strong><b>WHEN</b></strong>: Saturday\, July 29th from 10:30 - 12:00 PM ET<
 /p><p>Here's the schedule: </p><ul><li>10:30 AM -10:45 AM: FREE food! </li>
 <li>10:45 AM -11:00 AM: Opening Remarks</li><li>11:00 – 11:50 AM: Electrify
 Everything Roadshow Workshop<ul><li>What is the Inflation Reduction Act (IR
 A)?</li><li>IRA Tax Credits and Rebates </li><li>IRA for Tax-Exempt Entitie
 s  </li><li>Electric Vehicles</li><li>Home Electrification Improvements </l
 i><li>How do I advocate for state and local action?</li></ul></li><li>11:50
  AM - 12 noon: conclusion and next steps</li></ul><h2><b><strong><b><a href
 ="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/54588/data/1">RSVP today!</a></b><
 /strong></b></h2><br><b><strong><br></strong></b>
