 an equity study that reviewed practices and policies of the county and Park
  Authority.</span><br>Now they are accepting public comments! We want to ma
 ke sure everyone has a chance to learn this critical history and speak out 
 for justice\, healthy ecosystems and strong community outreach. <br><br>Can
  you join us on March 18th at 7:00 PM for a virtual call?<br><br>Hear direc
 tly from the Park Authority as well as coalition advocates. We will summari
 ze the study’s results and give you everything you need to know to prepare 
 and submit your comment.
