DESCRIPTION:CCAN Outreach at EPW Pride Festival in Manassas!<br><p>Come do 
 outreach with us at our booth at the Equality Prince William Pride Festival
  in Manassas\, VA on Saturday\, May 17! We will be talking to community mem
 bers about ways to take action on climate\, and gathering <a href="https://
 act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/79336/petition/1" target="_blank">petition</
 a> signatures for future Make Polluters Pay legislation in Virginia.</p><p>
 The festival runs from 12pm-4pm\, and we hope you can join us to help with 
 outreach for as long as you can (at least 2 hours would be great). <b>EMAIL
  TING AT <a href="mailto:TING@CHESAPEAKECLIMATE.ORG">TING@CHESAPEAKECLIMATE
 .ORG</a></b> about approximately when you plan on coming\, and we'll provid
 e training materials and connect you with our volunteer leads.</p><p>In ord
 er to build our people-powered climate movement\, we need people like you t
 o come out and help with our petition campaign to Make Polluters Pay!</p>
