  change and its impacts.</li><li>Education and networking community engagem
 ent are important first steps!</li></ul><p>Join us for an exciting in-perso
 n event at <strong>The Lot\, Across Waterfront Station</strong>! Our <stron
 g>All Hands on Deck Climate Action &amp\; Disaster Preparedness Community E
 ngagement Fair</strong> is the perfect opportunity to come together and mak
 e a difference. Connect with like-minded individuals\, learn about climate 
 action\, and get prepared for disasters. This fair is all about engaging ou
 r community and taking action for a better future. Don't miss out on this c
 hance to be part of the solution. Mark your calendars and get ready to make
  a positive impact!</p>
