DESCRIPTION:RSVP: <a href="https://actionnetwork.org/events/defend-rggi-pub
 lic-comment-writing-party/">https://actionnetwork.org/events/defend-rggi-pu
 blic-comment-writing-party/</a><br><br>Description: <span>Governor Youngkin
  continues his attacks on Virginia’s climate progress. He stacked the Air P
 ollution Control Board with 4 appointees. They ALL VOTED TO REMOVE VA FROM 
 RGGI.</span><p>Now they are hearing public comments on that disastrous deci
 sion.</p><p><strong><b>Join us to make your voice heard!</b></strong></p><p
 >Meeting agenda:</p><ul><li><p>5 mins intros</p></li><li><p>15 mins policy 
 presentation and Q&amp\;A -- including Megan Root\, sustainability program 
 assistant for Roanoke\, who will speak about what RGGI means for Roanoke\, 
 specifically the Weatherization Deferral and Repair funds</p></li><li><p>10
  mins how to write a comment and navigate Townhall -- Hunter Noffsinger</p>
 </li><li><p>20 mins breakout session</p></li><li><p>5 mins wrap up</p></li>
 </ul><p>This is a collaboration with CCAN\, the League of Conservation Vote
 rs\, Nature Forward\, and Appalachian Voices.</p>
