DESCRIPTION:<p>Every year\, the Public Service Commission (PSC) has “Perfor
 mance Oversight Hearings” which you can think of as the agency’s annual per
 formance review with the DC Council. These public hearings are a chance for
  the public to tell the Councilmembers about what you think of the PSC! It’
 s time for us to show up! <b><u>Join us to bring to light the public servic
 e commissioner’s failure to ensure just and reasonable rates\, and plan acc
 ording to the District’s climate commitments. </u></b></p><p>Let CCAN know 
 if you plan to testify at the PSC performance oversight hearings. We'll upd
 ate you when it is time to RSVP with the council\, share talking points and
  updates on the hearing agenda\, and share how to find us on hearing day!<b
 > </b></p><p><b>Save the date: </b></p><p>Friday\, February 27th\; Between 
 9:30 - 5pm [More timing info to come] </p><p><b><a href="https://actionnetw
 ork.org/events/psc-hearing" target="_blank">RSVP today!</a></b></p><p><br><
 /p>
