DESCRIPTION:Join CCAN as we enjoy collect petition signatures to Stop Proje
 ct Pipes -once and for all- through legislation! <b> <a href="https://www.g
 oogle.com/url?q=https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/86067/data/1&amp\;sa
 =D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1754166734067477&amp\;usg=AOvVaw2PWAN1umS6
 5psMG3VPB4v7" target="_blank"><u>RSVP here.</u></a></b><br><br><b>Where:</b
 > 50 Massachusetts Avenue Northeast Washington\, DC <br><b>When:</b> 11:30 
 - 1:30pm<br><br>For the past few years\, we&#39\;ve been pushing hard for t
 he PSC to end the wasteful and dangerous methane gas spending known as Proj
 ect Pipes. After disrupting business as-usual at the PSC\, it&#39\;s time t
 o up the ante. Let&#39\;s introduce legislation that not protects ratepayer
 s from exorbitant and unfair bills\, kickstarts clean energy pilot projects
 \, and ends project pipes once and for all!<br><br>To prove to Councilmembe
 rs that DC really cares\, we&#39\;ll need to demonstrate that their constit
 uents care - that&#39\;s where YOU come in. Join us to collect petition sig
 natures and build support in priority districts. As a special treat\, each 
 volunteer will receive a FREE snack on CCAN! No tabling experience necessar
 y\, we&#39\;ll do a quick training on-site.<br><br>Please reach out to Ayla
  (<a href="mailto:aylaf@chesapeakeclimate.org" target="_blank">aylaf@chesap
 eakeclimate.org</a>) with any questions or accommodations.
