  this celebration to reflect on and discuss community\, nature\, and belong
 ing. \n\nJoin us on April 22nd at 10 AM to get a glimpse of East African cu
 lture\, and engage in a larger conversation about nature and the global mov
 ement for environmental justice. We invite you to attend as we connect with
  nature and enjoy the coffee practices of the East African diaspora here in
  Virginia.
