CREATED:20230407T191416Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Join CCAN supporters from across Virginia for our
  Action Member Organizing Mini-Series!</b></strong></p><p>This month we are
  beginning a two part Organizing Skills Mini-Series focused on the grassroo
 ts fight against the Virginia RIPOFF Project.</p><p>To start\, we will host
  a training on the VRP’s environmental inequities and how canvassing can be
  a tool to build grassroots power. Then\, at our May meetup\, we'll train e
 veryone on how to run a door-to-door canvassing campaign. Plus\, we can hel
 p you travel to Hampton Roads for a CCAN outreach weekend with Charles on M
 ay 20. There you can apply your new skills alongside community members figh
 ting this pipeline in their backyards.</p><p><strong><b>Join us via Zoom on
  Thursday\, April 20\, at 7:00 PM\, to hear the latest and hone your organi
 zing skills!</b></strong></p><p><b>Here are the Zoom details for this event
 .</b> For the safety of our Zoom meetings\, please don’t share this link or
  post it on social media.</p><br><strong>Join on Zoom</strong>: <a href="ht
 tps://us06web.zoom.us/j/88030082675">https://us06web.zoom.us/j/88030082675<
 /a><br><p><strong>Meeting ID</strong>: 880 3008 2675</p><p>We recommend you
  join by your computer as there will be a visual component to this presenta
 tion. But\, you can also join by phone:</p><p><strong>One tap mobile: </str
