DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Join us for CCAN's </b></strong><strong><b>Baltim
 ore Action Team Meeting </b></strong></p><p>Join your friends and neighbors
  for next week's Baltimore Action Team Meeting.</p><p>We are building a wor
 king-class movement to stand up for our climate and our neighbors right her
 e in Baltimore. We will discuss important climate and electrification updat
 es\, review upcoming events\, and brainstorm ways to uplift climate stories
  in marginalized communities. Learn about how YOU can get involved by joini
 ng us for our monthly meeting! </p><p><strong><b>Join us for good FREE food
  and even better company in Baltimore on Wednesday\, July 30th\, at 7:00 PM
  in Downtown Baltimore\, or virtually on Zoom.</b></strong></p><p><strong><
 b>Address and Zoom info will be sent to all RSVPs. </b></strong></p><p><str
 ong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/85576/data/1">RSVP t
 oday! </a></b></strong></p><p><strong><br></strong></p>
