DESCRIPTION:<p>Join CCAN\, Delegate Charkoudian\, MD LCV and friends at Pow
 er in the Park to learn about</p><ul><li>Saving Energy</li><li>Lowering you
 r Energy Bills</li><li>Utility Assistance</li><li>Clean Energy</li><li>Heal
 thy Housing</li></ul><p>This third annual event is hosted by Delegate Lorig
  Charkoudian in coordination with Community Health &amp\; Empowerment throu
 gh Education &amp\; Research (CHEER) to connect the Long Branch community w
 ith energy assistance\, weatherization\, and community solar programs.</p><
 p>It’s free and open to the public on Thursday\, June 1\, from 6 – 8 pm at 
 the New Hampshire Estates Park – and it will have food and kid-friendly act
 ivities and games. </p><br><a href="https://www.mdlcv.org/event/power-in-th
 e-park">https://www.mdlcv.org/event/power-in-the-park</a>
