 ">zander@chesapeakeclimate.org</a>\, or </b><a href="mailto:lisa@vcnva.org"
  target="_blank">lisa@vcnva.org</a><span> </span><br><br>Description: <span
 >VCN will work to make it easy for you to lobby for the critical environmen
 tal action that matters most to you. Leading up to Conservation Lobby Day\,
  VCN will share resources on how to advocate\, provide talking points for e
 nvironmental policy solutions\, and schedule meetings with your legislators
 .</span><p>Join us in the Capital of Virginia as we kick off this year’s an
 nual Conservation Lobby Day at the Capitol Belltower on Tuesday\, Jan. 31st
 \, from 8-9 AM. Attend lobby meetings with your legislators and fellow advo
 cates throughout the morning. Then\, we will wrap up at St. Paul’s to recap
  a day well spent and plan our next steps.</p><p>In addition to the program
 \, registration includes coffee\, light breakfast\, and lunch at the event.
 </p>
