 utes the climate\, our lungs\, and our bank accounts. And they want the PSC
  to approve their egregious plan before this year is up. District residents
  deserve better than unwillingly\, and often unknowingly\, paying for syste
 ms that will hurt current and future generations of DC’ers. </p><p>Good new
 s is that we’ve got plans to stop them\, but it is going to take all of us.
