 /alexlibraryva.org/event/8724962</a><br><br>Description: <span>The campaign
  to buy solar panels is open until August 30! Solar United Neighbors will e
 xplain how it works\, what the options are and the next steps for upgrading
  your home with solar energy.</span><br><br><br><p></p><p><a href="https://
 solarswitch.com/en/virginia/home">Solar Switch</a> is a DC Metro bulk purch
 ase solar panel campaign. By working together\, the group has simplified th
 e solar panel pricing\, buying and installation process. We welcome back\, 
 Ben Hoyne\, Solar United Neighbors' Virginia Program Director\, who will go
  over what you need to know and answer questions to help you make the best 
 decision for your home and budget.</p><p>Solar Switch is open to anyone in 
 Northern Virginia\, DC\, Montgomery\, Frederick\, and Prince George's count
 ies.</p><p>Please register to attend this virtual event. </p><p>Contact Meg
 an at <a href="mailto:mzimmerman@alexlibraryva.org">mzimmerman@alexlibraryv
 a.org</a> for more information. </p>
