DESCRIPTION:RSVP: <a href="https://fy25budgetadvocacy.rsvpify.com/?security
 Token=RfoWZqYpREg7Cj4dyIFpcY8uQrXekBvZ">https://fy25budgetadvocacy.rsvpify.
 com/?securityToken=RfoWZqYpREg7Cj4dyIFpcY8uQrXekBvZ</a><br><br>Description:
  <span>The unified Northern Virginia Affordable Housing Alliance and the Al
 liance for Housing Solutions are hosting a virtual Local Budget Advocacy wo
 rkshop on Thursday\, February 22\, 2023\, from 7pm - 8:30 pm.</span><p>The 
 event's goal is to explore the process of advocating for greater housing re
 sources across all five Northern Virginia jurisdictions. Alice Hogan will s
 hare broad strategies to use in your own jurisdiction and you will hear jur
 isdictional-specific updates from grass-roots advocates and organizations i
 n Alexandria\, Arlington\, Fairfax\, Loudoun and Prince William. English-Sp
 anish Interpretation will be offered.</p>
