DESCRIPTION:<b>How Vanguard\, the world's #1 investor in fossil fuels\, is 
 linked to the Mountain Valley Pipeline. </b><br><br>This webinar will cover
 : <br><ul><li>What is an asset manager? </li><li>What is Vanguard?</li><li>
 What are bonds?</li><li>The difference between banks and asset managers for
  campaigning purposes </li><li>How Vanguard is linked to the Mountain Valle
 y Pipeline</li></ul><span>This webinar is open to the public\, in particula
 r communities that have been resisting the Mountain Valley Pipeline\, and a
 re wanting to learn more about asset managers and how they are funding the 
 Mountain Valley Pipeline.There will be a more in-depth Mountain Valley Pipe
 line-specific webinar in March to dive even deeper into these financial tie
 s.On the call we will have the Vanguard S.O.S. campaign\, POWHR (Protect Ou
 r Water\, Heritage\, Rights)\, and EQAT (Earth Quaker Action Team).</span>
