DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Calling all Hampton Roads climate advocates and c
 hange-makers!</b></strong></p><p>If you’re looking to take on responsibilit
 y and work with a group of inspiring dedicated climate activists to make a 
 difference in Hampton Roads\, our action team is the right place for you. <
 /p><p>Our next meeting is scheduled for <strong><b>Sunday\, April 13\, from
  1pm-3pm in downtown Norfolk. </b></strong>Expect icebreakers\, snacks\, an
 d real discussions about how to make a difference in Hampton Roads climate 
 advocacy. </p><p>Our next meeting will primarily be focused on the followin
 g:</p><ul><li>Local campaign planning and updates</li><li>Community event p
 lanning and updates</li><li>Advocacy needs and other regional updates</li><
 /ul><p>This meeting will be hybrid to accommodate members who can't make it
  in-person\, but want to join the meeting online. Snacks and refreshments w
 ill be provided for those who attend in person!</p><p>Don’t miss out—secure
  your spot today and be a part of something transformative!</p><h1><b><stro
 ng><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/81759/data/1">RSVP to
 day for the location and virtual link!</a></b></strong></b></h1>
