DESCRIPTION:<p>In 2020 we passed landmark clean energy legislation here in 
 Virginia. The Virginia Clean Economy Act set us on a path to a 100% renewab
 le energy economy and phased out fossil fuels. </p><p>Each year since its p
 assage we’ve defended this legislation against attacks. This year is no dif
 ferent. We’ve seen more than a dozen attack bills that would reclassify dir
 ty energy and false solutions as “renewables” and reverse our plan to phase
  out coal and gas plants. They’ve gotten disturbingly far.  So we need to m
 ake sure our legislators know that Virginians won’t stand for it.</p><p>Tha
 t’s why we will rally in front of the General Assembly and then do legislat
 or visits to make sure they know that we aren’t going back!</p><p></p><ul><
 li>10am: Rally at the Belltower\, 101 N 9th St\, Richmond\, VA 23219</li><l
 i>11am: Legislator visits</li></ul><p></p><p><em><strong><b><a href="https:
 //act.ccanactionfund.org/page/78688/data/1" target="_blank">RSVP now! </a><
 /b></strong></em></p><p><em><strong><br></strong></em></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250128T195414Z
LOCATION:101 N 9th St\, Richmond\, VA 23219\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:No Going Back! VCEA Defense! Rally and Legislator Visits [In-Person
  Event in Richmond]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
