DESCRIPTION:<p>Flooding is one of the most common impacts of climate change
 \, especially in Virginia. <a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/
 71414/data/1">Let’s learn and discuss the topic together!</a></p><p>If you'
 re curious about how climate impacts local flood risks\, join us to learn a
 bout what has been done and what could be done to help keep our communities
  safe. FREE lunch will be provided. RSVP now to join us on the 17th!  </p><
 p><strong><b>What</b></strong>: NoVa Flood Impacts Roundtable and Lunch<br>
 <strong><b>Where</b></strong>: Venture X Building\, 3060 Williams Dr. Fairf
 ax VA 22031\, Cherry Blossom Room on the third floor<br><strong><b>When</b>
 </strong>: August 17th\, 2024 12:00pm - 1:30pm<br><b>Parking</b>: You can p
 ark in any unmarked spot and the parking garage for free. </p><p><b><a href
 ="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/71414/data/1">RSVP today!</a></b><
 /p><p><br></p>
