UID:7l1dqfa0df8q965nhbppd9ml9r@google.com
CREATED:20260410T184937Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>What’s happening? </b></strong>Virginia’s lawmake
 rs did not pass a budget for next year. They will meet for a special sessio
 n on 4/23 to try again. Data center clean energy standards are a HUGE part 
 of the budget negotiation. </p><p><strong><b>What can we do? </b></strong>F
 lood budget conferees’ inboxes with constituent emails pushing for strong a
 ction on data centers!</p><p><strong><b>Join CCAN Action Fund and the Virgi
 nia League of Conservation Voters for a lunchtime virtual action call.</b><
 /strong> We will give you the latest political update and help you craft yo
 ur personal email to your legislator. </p><p><strong><b>WHEN</b></strong>: 
 Thursday\, April 16\, 12:00 - 12:30 PM ET on Zoom</p><p><em><strong><b><a h
 ref="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/96649/data/1">RSVP now for the Zoo
 m link! </a></b></strong></em></p><p><em><strong><br></strong></em></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260410T184949Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:No Dirty Data Centers in the Budget: Virtual Action Call
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
