 trol</span></li><li><span>rooftop solar</span></li><li><span>EV\, hybrid\, 
 EV home charger</span></li><li><span>heat pump water heater</span></li><li>
 <span>ancient\, 30+ year old electric clothes dryer</span></li></ul> <br><b
 r>then\, save the date\, mark your calendar\, register!  We can't wait to s
 ee you!!<br><br> <br><br>Consult with solar reps from SkyNRG\, energy audit
 ors from Home Energy Medics and your neighbors to learn how the process was
  for them.<br><br> <br><br>WHAT: Electrify Everything Showcase<br><br>WHEN:
  Saturday October 7th 11am - 1:00pm<br><br>WHERE: Leesburg (address provide
 d upon registration)<br><br> <br><br>Make sure to arrive by 11:00am because
  we will kick off the showcase with an introductory presentation for folks 
 wondering where to get started electrifying their home.
