DESCRIPTION:<p>Please consider joining us for<a href="https://act.chesapeak
 eclimate.org/page/95901/data/1"> CCAN’s April 757 Climate Action Team meeti
 ng and Earth Day celebration</a>! Here are the event details below:</p><p><
 strong>What</strong>: 757 Climate Action Team Meeting </p><p><strong>When</
 strong>: SATURDAY\, April 4th\, 1:00 PM - 3:00 PM</p><p><strong>Where</stro
 ng>: <b> </b>Campostella Square Park\, 2019 Windy Rd\, Chesapeake\, VA 2332
 4<br></p><p>***We have a new location! Our 2026 CAT park series will begin 
 this month as the weather is finally warming up :) For as long as the weath
 er permits\, we will meet in a new city park each month! I hope you enjoy t
 his opportunity to explore more beautiful parks in our region!</p><p><em><s
 trong>Snacks and refreshments will be provided in-person!</strong></em> </p
 ><p><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/95901/data/1"><b>RSVP A
 T THIS LINK!</b></a></p><p><br></p><p>We can’t wait to see you there! Feel 
 free to invite your friends and family for this Earth Day fun\, too!</p><p>
 Have any questions in the meantime? Contact CCAN’s Hampton Roads Organizing
  Fellow\, Michelle Ueltschi\, at <a href="mailto:michelleu@chesapeakeclimat
 e.org" target="_blank">michelleu@chesapeakeclimate.org</a> </p>
