  a 54-mile methane pipeline proposed to run through Virginia and North Caro
 lina. Now through June 6\, the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission is acce
 pting "scoping" comments on the project to help FERC know what should be in
 cluded in their environmental assessment of the pipeline.</p><p><b><a href=
