DESCRIPTION:"Join 350 &amp\; partners on Sunday\, November 19th at 1:30 PST
  / 4:30 EST for a webinar\, “Healing this Broken Land: Indigenous Leadershi
 p in the Face of the Climate Crisis.” We will shed light on the often-overl
 ooked impact climate change has on Indigenous Peoples globally. And we make
  the connection between the Doctrine of Discovery as the root of colonizati
 on\, war and the current climate crisis.<br><br>As we approach the day some
  call ‘thanksgiving’ and some call ‘thanks-taking\,’ we are reminded of the
  need to oppose colonization\, land theft\, genocide. Uplifting Indigenous 
 sovereignty is key to peace and justice and ending the climate catastrophe.
  Our movements must collectively vision a path forward that uproots dominat
 ion and restores connection\, harmony and balance.<br><br>ASL\, Spanish int
 erpretation &amp\; live captioning will be provided during the webinar. <br
 ><b><br></b><br><b>Register today at <a href="http://tinyurl.com/HealingBro
 kenLand">tinyurl.com/HealingBrokenLand</a>. </b><br><br>Sponsors: <a href="
 https://www.instagram.com/Tonatierra_org/">@Tonatierra_org</a>\, <a href="h
 ttps://www.instagram.com/AmericanIndianLawAlliance/">@AmericanIndianLawAlli
 ance</a>\, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/EasternWoodlandsRematriation/
 ">@EasternWoodlandsRematriation</a>\, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/Ho
 northeEarth/">@HonortheEarth</a>\, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/Hawai
 iPeaceandJustice/">@HawaiiPeaceandJustice</a>\, Indigenous Solidarity Netwo
 rk\, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/_CatalystProject_/">@_CatalystProje
 ct_</a>\, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/ShowingUpforRacialJustice/">@S
 howingUpforRacialJustice</a> (SURJ)\, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/35
 0us/">@350us</a>\, and <a href="https://www.instagram.com/NunsandNones/">@N
 unsandNones</a> Land Justice." <br><br>From 350 US
