DESCRIPTION:<br><p><strong><b>It’s been one year since President Biden sign
 ed the historic Inflation Reduction Act\, an unprecedented investment into 
 clean energy</b></strong>. Since the signing\, over 211 clean energy projec
 ts have been announced across 38 states—a true clean energy revolution! Or 
 so we’re hoping. So far\, countless clean energy projects have faced challe
 nges with grid transmission\, interconnection\, and siting. The clean energ
 y revolution is at risk of being stopped right in its tracks.</p><p>That’s 
 why you’re invited to an exciting webinar called on Tuesday\, September 12 
 at 7:00 PM ET called “Clean Energy Revolution: What’s the Next Big Step?” A
 t this webinar you’ll hear from experts on the most impactful policies for 
 responsible transmission\, interconnection\, and siting reforms.</p><ul><li
 ><strong><b>WHAT</b></strong>: Clean Energy Revolution: What’s the Next Big
  Step?</li><li><strong><b>WHEN: </b></strong>Tuesday\, September 12\, 7:00 
 PM ET</li><li><strong><b>WHO</b></strong>: Experts from CCAN\, Advanced Ene
 rgy United\, and more</li><li><strong><b>ZOOM LINK:</b></strong> <a href="h
 ttps://us06web.zoom.us/j/87487423601?pwd=OW92N2pSbnhscG5WQU90Z3Nsb0ZiUT09">
 <u>https://us06web.zoom.us/j/87487423601?pwd=OW92N2pSbnhscG5WQU90Z3Nsb0ZiUT
 09</u></a></li></ul><h3><strong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.o
 rg/page/56015/data/1"><u>RSVP TODAY!</u></a></b></strong></h3>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230823T183432Z
