 s about how to make a difference in Hampton Roads climate advocacy. </p><p>
 Our next meeting will primarily be focused on the following:</p><ul><li>30-
 minute art build! Come together with other climate activists to paint\, dra
 w\, or cut out signs for CCAN’s upcoming climate rally in Richmond :) </li>
