 >Meet other climate activists in the area!</li><li>Help plan our 757 plunge
 \, climate rally in Richmond\, and Lobby day on February 17th!</li><li>Snac
 ks and treats!!</li></ul><p>This meeting will be <strong><b>hybrid </b></st
 rong>to accommodate members who can't make it in-person\, but want to join 
