DESCRIPTION:<p><b>RSVP</b>: <a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/77
 187/data/1">https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/77187/data/1</a></p><p><spa
 n><b>Description</b>: </span><span>Starting on January 8th\, Virginia’s ele
 cted officials will gather in Richmond for the 2025 General Assembly. They 
 will have a short amount of time to pass every single bill they can in 2025
 .</span></p>Those days during session move FAST\, and we need as many peopl
 e as possible to make sure our legislators pass bills for clean energy and 
 climate justice. That's why we need YOU.<br><br>Can you join our virtual cl
 imate champions team? For an hour a week in January and February (or as muc
 h time as you have to give) you can make a BIG difference in passing climat
 e legislation!<br><p>We meet two times a week\, just before important commi
 ttee hearings for key climate legislation. During the call we explain the k
 ey bill of the day\, and which legislators need to hear from the community.
  Then we give you clear ways to help move that legislator to get the climat
 e bill passed (or the anti-climate bill defeated)! </p><p>Can you help us b
 y signing up to be a grassroots climate champion for the 2025 General Assem
 bly Session?</p><p>We will meet every Monday from 12:30 - 1:00 pm and every
  Wednesday from 5:30 - 6:00 pm starting on Monday January 13th and ending W
 ednesday February 19th. </p><p><span>RSVP now!</span></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20241212T210202Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Grassroots Climate Champions - 2025 General Assembly
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
