DESCRIPTION:<p>Six days before Virginia heads to the polls\, join us for on
 e of the most important meetups of the year\; a time to ground ourselves\, 
 get inspired\,and prepare for this decisive moment. Our featured guest\, <b
 >Victoria Higgins\, CCAN Action Fund’s Virginia Director</b>\, will walk us
  through what’s at stake in these elections and how results here in Central
  Virginia can shape the future of clean energy\, jobs\, and climate policy 
 statewide and nationally. </p><p>We’ll also share short updates on ongoing 
 campaigns that keep our region moving cleanly and safely. </p><p>Dinner\, s
 nacks\, and refreshments provided! </p><p>Bring a friend or join online\, y
 our presence\, voice\, and action truly matter. <br></p><p><b><a href="http
 s://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/89622/data/1">RSVP today for the location a
 nd Zoom link!</a></b></p>
