DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>In September\, CCAN is joining activists around t
 he world in showing that SOLAR power is the most disruptive\, revolutionary
  energy source for good in the world</b></strong>. These events will take p
 lace all across America.</p><p>The weekend will kick off with an historic E
 V parade around the US Capitol in Washington DC on Friday\, September 19. O
 ur plan is to have at least two dozen decorated EV cars\, E-bikes\, and E-s
 cooters follow a pre-selected loop in front of the Capitol for at least 30 
 minutes with pro-solar messaging.</p><p>Here are the details:</p><ul><li>Ca
 rs gather at Parking Lot 3 at RFK stadium (2400 E Capitol St NE\, Washingto
 n\, DC 20003 US) at 11:00 AM ET where we will apply decorations\, hear quic
 k speeches\, etc then make the one-mile drive together to the Capitol\, arr
 iving at noon.</li><li>E-scooters and bikes can meet at the Capitol on thir
 d street next to the west lawn of the capitol at noon. Bikes\, etc are enco
 uraged to display pro-solar signage and decorations too.</li><li>We will co
 ntinue a loop parade route for 30-60 minutes with reporters and supporters 
 on the Mall on 3rd Street NW taking pictures as we pass by.</li></ul><h3><s
 trong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/87850/data/1">RSVP
  today!</a></b></strong></h3><br><strong><br></strong>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250908T183349Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:EV Rally at the US Capitol for Sun Day [In-Person Event]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
