  enormous rate hike proposal!</b></strong></p><p>Sign up below testify at t
 he rate case public hearings. We'll coordinate with sign ups to make sure y
 ou receive our suggested talking points\, get updates about the hearing age
 nda\, and know how to find us on hearing day. Here's where the hearings wil
 l be held: </p><ul><li><strong><b>Thursday\, April 10\, 2025: </b></strong>
 5:30-7:30 PM: Benning / Dorothy I. Height Neighborhood Library\, 3935 Benni
 ng Road\, NE\, Meeting Room 1</li><li><strong><b>Monday\, April 21\, 2025:<
 /b></strong> 5:00-7:00 PM: Petworth Neighborhood Library\, 4200 Kansas Aven
 ue\, NW\, Meeting Room 1</li><li><strong><b>Tuesday\, April 29\, 2025:</b><
 /strong> 6:00 - 8:00 PM: DCPSC Hearing Room\, 1325 G Street\, NW\, Suite 80
 0</li></ul><p>You can testify at one hearing\, or all three! </p><p><strong
 ><b><a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/80783/data/1"><u>RSVP toda
 y!</u></a></b></strong></p>
