DESCRIPTION:<p>Join Illuminate Maryland and CCAN Action Fund on Friday\, Ma
 rch 20th for Student Climate Lobby Day! At 11am\, we will gather at Lawyer&
 #39\;s Mall in Annapolis for a rally and press event in front of the Maryla
 nd State House to call on our elected leaders to stand up for our climate a
 nd pass critical legislation like the Affordable Solar Act. </p><p>Once leg
 islators have entered the State House\, we will travel to the Lowe House Of
 fice Building to prepare for meetings with legislators and their staff. Fre
 e lunch and refreshments will be provided.</p><p>Agenda:</p><ul><li>11:00am
  - Arrival at Lawyer&#39\;s Mall</li><li>11:30am - Press Event and Rally</l
 i><li>12:15pm - Travel to House Office Building Room 180 and Lunch</li><li>
 12:45am - 2pm - Meetings with Legislators and Lit-Drop</li></ul><h2><b><str
 ong><b><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://act.ccanactionfund.org
 /page/94976/data/1&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1773862776483608
 &amp\;usg=AOvVaw1Ppp1U9SkU0_Igkwp4kLPI" target="_blank">RSVP today!</a></b>
 </strong></b></h2><br><b><strong><br></strong></b>
