DESCRIPTION:<p>Join Josh Kurtz and Mike Tidwell for a lively conversation a
 bout climate change\, Maryland Governor Wes Moore\, the General Assembly\, 
 new books\, and what’s next for Josh after Maryland Matters.</p><p>If you o
 rdered a copy of The Lost Trees of Willow Avenue: A Story of Climate and Ho
 pe on One American Street with your RSVP\, you will be receiving it in the 
 mail in the coming weeks.<br><br>All proceeds go to support the work of the
  Chesapeake Climate Action Network (CCAN). Your support goes directly towar
 d our mission of building a people-powered climate movement and putting our
  region and nation on the path to climate stability. With your help\, CCAN 
 has the resources we need to handle the challenges ahead and to continue mo
 ving forward with climate solutions. We’ll continue to do everything we can
  to put us on the path to the clean energy future we and our children deser
 ve.</p><p>RSVP: <a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/83568/event
 /1">https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/83568/event/1</a></p><p>Must RSV
 P for zoom link</p>
