 reat people? Join CCAN at the South of the James Farmers Market.</p><p>This
  fall\, we’re spreading the word about the crucial need to increase funding
  for public transportation like buses\, trains\, and bikeable communities. 
 And we need YOUR help!</p><p><strong><b>WHAT</b></strong>: Table for public
  transportation at South of the James Farmers Market<br><strong><b>WHEN</b>
 </strong>: Sundays in October\, 10am-1pm. Please arrive by 9:45am<br><stron
