  </p><p>The Maryland General Assembly's legislative session concludes on Mo
 nday April 8. Find out what happened with various climate priorities\, what
  we plan to do next\, and how you can be involved.<br><br><strong><b>Sign u
 p now to join us Wednesday\, April 17 at 7:00 PM!</b></strong></p><p><stron
 g><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/65875/data/1">RSVP to 
 get Zoom details! </a></b></strong></p>
