 &amp\;utm_content=sia_webinar</a><br><br>Description:<br><br><br>Join Sierr
 a Club for a training series on May 16th and 23rd to learn about the latest
  ways you can take action to encourage Biden to deliver on nature-based cli
 mate solutions by enacting a meaningful rule protecting mature &amp\; old f
 orests.Meaningful public comments are hugely important to this process\, an
 d we&#39\;ll be going over how you write the most impactful comment and lea
 rn how to use your public narrative to influence our federal government and
  your community.On May 16th we&#39\;ll do a policy overview and public narr
 ative training\, then we&#39\;ll come back on May 23rd to submit our commen
 ts\, brainstorm ways to get our friends and family involved\, and go over w
 hat else Sierra Club is working on this Spring and Summer to protect lands\
 , water\, and wildlife.
