DESCRIPTION:<p dir="ltr">Join us for a FREE screening of <a href="https://h
 hc.fyi/underwater"><u>Underwater Projects</u></a>\, a film from Hip Hop Cau
 cus that honors and sheds light on how the climate crisis affects communiti
 es of color and offers solutions that achieve environmental justice.</p><p 
 dir="ltr">At our free screening\, there will be a discussion following the 
 film\, vegetarian snacks\, and a call to action for Hampton Roads. We’re ex
 cited to host a screening of this incredible film at the <b>Ryan Resilience
  Lab in Norfolk\, Virginia</b> on <b>August 12th</b> at 6:00 pm!</p><p dir=
 "ltr">This screening will be <b>hybrid</b> to accommodate members who can't
  make it in-person\, but want to watch online. <i>Snacks and refreshments w
 ill be provided for those who attend in person!</i></p><p dir="ltr">Don’t m
 iss out—secure your spot today and learn about the history of climate justi
 ce in Hampton Roads! We hope you can make it! </p><p dir="ltr"><b><a href="
 https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/86334/data/1"><u>RSVP today for free
 !</u></a></b></p>
