DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Calling CCAN’s DC climate advocates and change-ma
 kers: join our DC Activists Meeting on Thursday\, May 15 from 7:00 pm to 8:
 00 pm. </b></strong></p><p>Attend our monthly volunteer meeting to meet oth
 er activists\, hear regular campaign updates\, learn about upcoming actions
 \, and take an active role in planning our next steps. Whether you’re new t
 o our efforts or a longtime supporter\, these meetups offer a great introdu
 ction to our advocacy and provide an opportunity to learn more and deepen y
 our involvement.</p><h1><b><strong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimat
 e.org/page/82021/data/1">RSVP today!</a></b></strong></b></h1><br>Meetings 
 are held on the second Thursday of the month\, switching between in-person 
 and on Zoom. <p>This month\, we will be meeting in conference room 401-E at
  Martin Luther King Jr. Memorial Library (901 G St. NW) - right by the Gall
 ery Place metro station. <br></p>
