DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://actionnetwork.org/events/sun-day-nova-fcps-sol
 ar-electric-school-bus-celebration?referrer=group-chesapeake-climate-action
 -network&amp\;source=sundayviennabus" style="font-weight: bold\;">RSVP HERE
 </a><b>!</b><br><br>If you would like to volunteer at CCAN's table for this
  event\, please contact Ting at <b><a href="mailto:ting@chesapeakeclimate.o
 rg">ting@chesapeakeclimate.org</a>!</b><br><p>Start your Sun Day with sunsh
 ine and celebration! We’re marking the launch of the <strong><b>Fairfax Cou
 nty Public Schools solar initiative</b></strong>\, plus the arrival of <str
 ong><b>17 new electric school buses! </b></strong>Come learn more about the
  great work FCPS is doing to reduce their carbon footprint and meet their s
 ustainability goals.</p><p><strong><b></b></strong><strong><b></b></strong>
 <strong><b>This family-friendly party features:</b></strong><br>🎶 Live mus
 ic<br>🍧 Electric school bus-powered snow cones<br>📖 Solar story time<br>
 🌿 Student-led sustainability demos<br>🧠 Local climate group tables<br>📍 
 Don’t forget your Sun Day passport for prizes!<br><br>Sun Day is a global d
 ay of action on September 21st\, 2025\, celebrating the unstoppable rise of
  clean energy. We’ll come together to showcase the power of the sun and win
 d\, the energy sources that can power our world without pollution.<br><br>C
 o-hosted by CCAN\, Mothers Out Front\, and other partners. </p>
