DESCRIPTION:<p><u><b><a href="https://actionnetwork.org/events/rally-for-no
 -gas-plants">RSVP HERE</a></b></u></p><p>Join us to rally against Dominion'
 s proposed gas plant in Chesterfield County! We will be gathering in Woodbr
 idge\, in solidarity with our community members down in Chester who have be
 en fighting this gas plant proposal for two years now. Our rally coincides 
 with a critical public hearing happening on September 8 at the Department o
 f Environmental Quality (DEQ) down in central VA\, and we are gathering at 
 the DEQ's NoVA office to show them that people in NoVA care\, too! We stand
  in defense of the VCEA and our children's futures\, and we are saying NO G
 AS PLANTS!</p><p>Dominion Energy plans to build a gas plant in Chesterfield
  County and 5 additional new gas plants elsewhere in Virginia. These plants
  would lock us into decades of expensive fossil fuel infrastructure\, incre
 ase toxic air pollution\, and threaten our progress toward a clean energy f
 uture—all while driving up utility bills.</p><p>We need to show the DEQ tha
 t fossil fuels are NOT the future we envision for Virginia. Let’s show up\,
  get organized\, and stop this plant together.<br></p><p>We will be meeting
  at the edge of a parking lot in Noblewood Plaza\, then walking to the Depa
 rtment of Environmental Quality together as part of the event. Plug 14130 N
 oblewood Plaza\, Woodbridge into your GPS and you should find us gathering 
 by the parking lot and gearing up for our rally.<br><br>Please reach out to
  Ting\, <a href="mailto:ting@chesapeakeclimate.org" target="_blank">ting@ch
 esapeakeclimate.org</a>\, with questions or if you require transportation a
 ssistance. </p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250903T212945Z
LOCATION:14130 Noblewood Plaza\, Woodbridge\, VA 22193\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:NoVA Rally for No Gas Plants! [In-Person Event]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
