CREATED:20240624T153001Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>oin us for a sunny day of art\, nature\, and climate action 
 in Maymont Community Garden! CCAN is inviting YOU to come be a part of this
  fun community event where we will pot succulents\, paint the pots\, and ce
 lebrate our commitment to building a more sustainable future!</p><p><strong
 ><b>Who</b></strong>: All ages and skill levels are welcome!<br><strong><b>
 What</b></strong>: Paint pots\, plant succulents<br><strong><b>When</b></st
 rong>: Saturday June 29\, 11:00 AM<br><strong><b>Where</b></strong>: Commun
 ity Garden next to Treasure Island Skatepark: <a href="https://maps.app.goo
 .gl/Ee6xh5Ma2qFA8bV87" target="_blank">https://maps.app.goo.gl/Ee6xh5Ma2qFA
 8bV87</a></p><p>This is your chance to unleash your creativity\, connect wi
 th other climate-enthusiasts\, and contribute to a greener\, more beautiful
  community! Food\, refreshments\, and supplies will be provided. Just bring
  yourself and your energy!</p><p> </p><h2><b><strong><b><a href="https://ac
 t.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/69291/data/1" target="_blank">RSVP today!</a><
 /b></strong></b></h2>
