DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Calling all Hampton Roads climate advocates and c
 hange-makers!</b></strong></p><p>Our next 757 Climate Action Team meeting i
 s scheduled for <strong><b>Sunday\, August 17\, from 1:00 - 3:00 PM in down
 town Norfolk or online via Zoom</b></strong>. Expect icebreakers\, snacks\,
  and real discussions about how to make a difference in Hampton Roads clima
 te advocacy. </p><p>Our next meeting will primarily be focused on the follo
 wing:</p><ul><li>Local campaign planning and updates</li><li>Community even
 t planning and updates</li><li>Advocacy needs and other regional updates</l
 i></ul><p>Don’t miss out—secure your spot today and be a part of something 
 transformative!</p><h1><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/8595
 7/data/1">Sign up for our August action team meeting!</a></h1><br><br><br><
 b><strong><br></strong></b>
