DESCRIPTION:Description: This event is for CCAN's local chapter in Northern
  VA--the NOVA New Leaf Team. These monthly hybrid meetings allow team membe
 rs to share updates\, collaborate on campaigns and build relationships. <br
 ><br>We will <b>start our hybrid meeting promptly at 2:15pm</b>. <b>If you 
 are attending in person\, arrive by 2pm</b> so you have time to set up your
  laptop and socialize :). The zoom link for remote attendees will be provid
 ed upon request.<br><br>Please email Ting Waymouth\, Northern Virginia Orga
 nizer\, at <a href="mailto:ting@chesapeakeclimate.org" target="_blank">ting
 @chesapeakeclimate.org</a>\, if you would like to join!   <br><br>Fill out 
 an interest form for the NOVA New Leaf Team: <a href="https://act.chesapeak
 eclimate.org/page/49671/data/1" target="_blank">https://act.chesapeakeclima
 te.org/page/49671/data/1</a>
