UID:3dsnmsl8ac345kudmtgpc5k722@google.com
CREATED:20250711T220458Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><b><b>Join us as we write letters to the Public Service Comm
 ission to say: No Blank Checks to BGE!</b></b></p><p>The Public Service Com
 mission (PSC) just released its first order to reduce the use of gas in hom
 es and reign in unnecessary utility profiteering on new gas infrastructure.
  In this order\, they determined that new gas lines need to be paid for by 
 the users--not by burdening all utility customers with the cost of expensiv
 e\, polluting gas. This is a big win! But we need to share our stories in o
 rder to support their work and move forward with even more ambitious regula
 tions.</p><p><strong><b>That's why we're gathering on Monday\, July 21st to
  discuss the PSC order and how to write comments to show your support. Join
  us for free food and possibly a visit from a special guest!</b></strong></
 p><p>RSVP Here: <a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/85533/data/
 1" target="_blank">https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/85533/data/1</a><
 br><br>Questions? Please contact Dustin at <a href="mailto:dustin@chesapeak
 eclimate.org" target="_blank">dustin@chesapeakeclimate.org</a></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250714T192619Z
LOCATION:Impact Hub Baltimore\, 10 E North Ave Suite 5\, Baltimore\, MD 212
 02\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:MD - PSC Comment Writing Party in Baltimore
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
