CREATED:20240723T145902Z
DESCRIPTION:With the Mountain Valley Pipeline\, unaddressed coal ash in our
  ports\, and billions in funding at stake this November\, how can we push f
 or equity and justice in addressing pollution\, flooding\, and community he
 alth in Hampton Roads?<br><br>This Thursday\, July 25th from 6-8pm\, join t
 he Chesapeake Climate Action Network\, the League of Conservation Voters\, 
 and the NAACP for an Environmental Justice Round Table talk in Virginia Bea
 ch. Together\, we will share stories\, express shared concerns\, and collab
 orate on community-driven solutions! <br><br>This is YOUR chance to connect
  with passionate individuals\, experienced organizers\, and local leaders t
 o strategize and combine efforts for meaningful change. Plus\, enjoy food a
 nd refreshments on us! Don't miss out on the opportunity to be a part of so
 mething transformative!<br><br>RSVP here: <a href="https://www.mobilize.us/
 lcvva/event/643857/">https://www.mobilize.us/lcvva/event/643857/</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240723T145902Z
LOCATION:809 S Military Highway Virginia Beach\, VA 23464
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Environmental Justice Round Table in VA Beach
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
