 b></strong>: Hattie Holmes Senior Wellness Center - 324 Kennedy St NW\, Was
 hington\, DC 20011</p><p><strong><b>When</b></strong>: Wednesday\, April 2n
 d: 12:30-1:30pm</p><h2><b><strong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate
