DESCRIPTION:<p><b><a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/93924/data/1
 " target="_blank">Join us for a community discussion about how and why we s
 hould make polluters pay for climate change in DC! </a></b></p><p>Calling a
 ll Ward 6 neighbors!  Join our community gathering to learn about our plan 
 to prepare DC for extreme weather caused by climate change – by making big 
 polluters foot the bill! </p><p>We’ll discuss the local and personal impact
 s of climate change: have you experienced more flooding\, extreme weather\,
  increased allergies\, or other weather events that make normal life more d
 ifficult? Are you concerned that our city infrastructure will not meet the 
 needs of our heating planet? Lastly\, do you agree that the greedy corporat
 ions who created this mess should be the ones to pay for the solutions? Joi
 n us to make your voice heard! </p><p><strong><b>When</b></strong>: Tuesday
 \, March 31\, 6:30-8:00 PM ET<br><strong><b>Where</b></strong>: Bonchon Nav
 y Yard - 1015 Half St SE\, Washington\, DC 20003</p><p>*Dinner is on us!</p
 ><i><b><a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/93924/data/1" target="_
 blank">RSVP today!</a></b></i><br><i><br></i>
