DESCRIPTION:<p>We are pleased to invite you to a community forum discussing
  the <strong>results of our 2024 Housing Report</strong>\, a collaboration 
 between <strong>La ColectiVA\, local residents\, and volunteers from Marymo
 unt University</strong>. This report highlights data and real stories of co
 mmunity members in Arlington who are at risk/affected by housing displaceme
 nt due to gentrification and other situations affecting neighborhoods in Ar
 lington.</p><br><p>Together\, we will:</p><ul><li><p>Review the key finding
 s from the 2024 Housing Report and how they impact our neighbors in Arlingt
 on.</p></li><li><p>Hear firsthand accounts from residents affected or at ri
 sk of displacement.</p></li><li><p>Discuss what we\, as a community\, can d
 o to advocate for fair housing and protect our neighbors from displacement.
 </p></li></ul><p>This is a chance to stand in solidarity with those impacte
 d\, learn more about housing injustice\, and find ways to take action. We h
 ope to see you there to join the conversation and support your community.</
 p><p><strong>Take Action:</strong> Please RSVP here: <a href="https://url10
 05.email.actionnetwork.org/ss/c/u001.jTd4CJP2oHMhBHdrjS9uukymv0oYzToTTrLpG8
 VEfA5Qh9yP9D1j8xxCtaNU7T-94BTv9xE147p9syr8kr8LaVwSMYdnH9wc_2i5WigXacEXVd1Uv
