DESCRIPTION:<p>Join Meredith from CCAN and The Washington Area Bicyclist As
 sociation for an fun bike ride where we will remove Invasive Vines along th
 e Marvin Gaye Trail.</p><p>Meet us at <strong><b>The Fields At RFK Campus</
 b></strong> at 10:00am for a eco-focused ride led by the D.C Trail Rangers 
 and Chesapeake Climate Action Network. Let’s pedal together to explore our 
 trails and enjoy the scenic beauty of the Marvin Gaye Trail. Don’t forget y
 our bike\, helmet\, water bottle and your enthusiasm!</p><p><a href="https:
 //www.eventbrite.com/e/bicyclists-against-invasive-vines-ride-to-marvin-gay
 e-trail-tickets-1217988338909?aff=oddtdtcreator">https://www.eventbrite.com
