 hange-makers!</b></strong></p><p>Our next 757 Climate Action Team meeting i
 s scheduled for <strong><b>Sunday\, June 15\, from 1:00 - 3:00 PM in downto
 wn Norfolk or online via Zoom</b></strong>. Expect icebreakers\, snacks\, a
 nd real discussions about how to make a difference in Hampton Roads climate
  advocacy. </p><p>Our next meeting will primarily be focused on the followi
 ng:</p><ul><li>Local campaign planning and updates</li><li>Community event 
 planning and updates</li><li>Advocacy needs and other regional updates</li>
 </ul><p>Don’t miss out—secure your spot today and be a part of something tr
 ansformative!</p><h1><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://act.ches
 apeakeclimate.org/page/84235/data/1&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust
