 d Middle School?! No way! </span></span></span></span></span></span></stron
 g><br><p><span><span><span><span><span><span>Virginia Natural Gas wants to 
 build a project that would leak methane and could increase negative health 
 impacts in an environmental justice community. </span></span></span></span>
 </span></span></p><p><span><span><span><span><span><span>That’s why we are 
 hosting a <strong>community door knocking day on Saturday June 14th from 10
