 /span></span></span></span></span></li>    <li><span><span><span><span><spa
 n><span>12:30 PM - 1:00 PM recap and share next steps</span></span></span><
 /span></span></span></li></ul><p><span><span><span><span><span><span>With y
 our help we will gather petition signatures from impacted residents to deli
 ver to City Council when they vote.</span></span></span></span></span></spa
 n></p><p><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span>Can you join?</span></
 span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>
