 make a difference! </p><p>On <strong><b>Wednesday\, January 15\, 2025</b></
 strong>\, VAIPL will partner with VICPP to host Day for All People 2025. Th
 e day will include workshops\, in-person meetings with legislators at the G
 eneral Assembly building\, plenaries\, and multiple opportunities for you t
 o network with other advocates from across the state. <br> </p><hr /><p><st
 rong><b><u>The Day at a Glance</u></b></strong><br>7:30 AM - Event check-in
  [A continental breakfast will be available]</p><p>8:30 AM - Opening Sessio
 n (in the Sanctuary)</p><p>10:00 AM - Meetings with State Senators</p><p>10
 :45 AM - Meetings with Delegates</p><p>11:30 AM - Lunch people will have an
  opportunity to gather with others from their area.</p><p>12:30 AM - Worksh
 ops I &amp\; II </p><p>3:00 PM - Closing and Dismissal</p><hr />
