DESCRIPTION:<span><span><span><span><br><span><span><span><span><span><span
 ><h2><span><span><strong><span>Join us for our Make Polluters Pay Canvasses
  in Montgomery County!</span></strong></span></span></h2></span></span></sp
 an></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><p><span><span><strong><spa
 n>July 18 from 3:00 PM to 8:00 PM in Shady Grove - <a href="https://ccan.li
 nk/2025-MoCo-Canvasses">RSVP for details</a></span></strong></span></span><
 /p></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><p><span>We've fough
 t too hard and too long for climate justice in Maryland to stop now. That's
  why we are not only continuing our work\, we're ramping up our efforts to 
 get even more Marylanders involved — and we need YOU! <span>Let's help get 
 the word out about climate justice\, including making polluters pay for the
 ir contributions to the climate crisis and getting toxic gas out of our hom
 es. </span><span><span><span><span><span>We'll also ask people to join CCAN
 !</span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span>Building the bigges
 t coalition possible will help make our people-powered climate movement mor
 e representative of the diverse communities in Maryland\, enable us to buil
 d powerful volunteer action teams\, and prepare us to have robust in-distri
 ct meetings with legislators to put pressure on them to support our priorit
 y issues. </span></p><h2><span><span><strong><span>RSVP today to knock door
 s or table for climate<br>and environmental justice! <a href="https://ccan.
 link/2025-MoCo-Canvasses">RSVP HERE</a>!</span></strong></span></span></h2>
 </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>
