CREATED:20250213T181510Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Environmental\, justice and faith groups were stunned earlie
 r this month to learn top Democratic lawmakers in Annapolis want to build o
 ne or more large gas-burning power plants in the state! They have introduce
 d legislation which\, if passed\, would make that happen.<strong><b>  </b><
 /strong></p><p>The organization that manages much of the mid Atlantic elect
 ricity grid – called PJM -- is dominated by utility interests. In recent ye
 ars\, PJM has wildly mismanaged the grid. As a result\, electricity prices 
 are going up in Maryland. To solve that problem – surprise! – PJM and the M
 aryland gas utilities want to build one or two massive gas-fired power plan
 ts in the state. The cost would be in the billions despite the fact that ch
 eaper\, faster and safer alternatives readily exist. We have to act fast to
  stop these gas plants!</p><p><strong><b>WHAT: </b></strong>Stop New Gas Pl
 ants in Maryland<br><strong><b>WHEN:</b></strong> Tuesday\, February 18\, 7
 :00 PM ET<br><strong><b>WHERE:</b></strong> Your computer! Zoom info provid
 ed after you RSVP.</p><h2><b><strong><b><a href="https://act.ccanactionfund
 .org/page/79368/data/1">RSVP today!</a></b></strong></b></h2><br><b><strong
 ><br></strong></b>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250217T154504Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Webinar: Stop New Gas Plants in MD
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
