DESCRIPTION:<br><p>RSVP Now:<a href="https://www.mobilize.us/ccanactionfund
 /event/746893/">https://www.mobilize.us/ccanactionfund/event/746893/</a></p
 ><p>Sign up to be a lobby captain: <a href="https://www.mobilize.us/ccanact
 ionfund/event/743218/">https://www.mobilize.us/ccanactionfund/event/743218/
 </a></p><p>Join over 150 people for lobby night in Annapolis on Monday\, Fe
 bruary 24\, from 5:30-8 PM at Asbury United Methodist Church located at 87 
 West St in Annapolis.</p><p>You and your lobbying team will meet with your 
 legislators\, meeting fellow CCAN members and volunteers from across the st
 ate\, and enjoy some pizza\, together.</p><p>We will have teams of voluntee
 rs meeting with their legislators to advocate for:</p><ul><li><p>The RENEW 
 Act to make polluters pay for their contributions to the climate crisis.</p
 ></li><li><p>The Better Buildings Act to electrify all new residential buil
 dings.</p></li><li><p>The Affordable\, Abundant Clean Energy Act so that we
  take control of utility bills by investing in clean energy.</p></li><li><p
 >Any climate justice bills your lobbying team is passionate about.</p></li>
 </ul>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250117T181649Z
LOCATION:87 West St\, Annapolis\, MD 21401\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Maryland Climate Lobby Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
