 ing things up a little bit and attending the event in the link below due to
  it being in a park AND covering one of this year's big issues: Data Center
 s.</p><p>Make sure to sign up on the link below\, AND let Ting\, CCAN's NoV
 A Organizer\, know you plan on coming! Email Ting at ting@chesapeakeclimate
 .org.</p><p><a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/walk-in-the-woods-trees-a
