DESCRIPTION:<p><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/85103/data/1
 "><strong><b>Join us for July 2025 </b></strong><strong><b>CCAN Power Hour 
 - FREE! </b></strong></a></p><p><br></p><p><strong><b>CCAN is investing in 
 volunteer leadership teams all across the Maryland\, Virginia\, Washington 
 DC region and beyond.</b></strong></p><p>Join our campaigns and help us ide
 ntify opportunities to take action on critical climate issues in your commu
 nity. This month's Power Hour is a great opportunity to learn how CCAN is b
 uilding support to address the climate crisis\, how you can get involved\, 
 and what it means to become an Action Member.</p><p><strong><b>SIGN UP for 
 Action Member Orientation</b></strong><br><strong><b>7 PM-8 PM ET on Tuesda
 y\, July 15\, 2025</b></strong></p><p><strong><b>​​​​This past year\, CCAN 
 recruited and developed dozens of volunteer leaders</b></strong> who are sp
 earheading public education campaigns to stop construction of fossil-fuel p
 ipelines\, build a team of young climate champions\, advocate for expanding
  public transit options\, protect our green spaces\, lobby legislators to p
 ass historic climate legislation\, and more. These volunteers have taken on
  significant leadership roles and have become critical contributors to the 
 success of our movement!</p><p><strong><b>Sign up now and see how you can g
 et more involved.</b></strong> Thanks for your support. We can't do it with
 out you!<br> </p><p><strong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/p
 age/85103/data/1">RSVP to get Zoom details! </a></b></strong></p><p><strong
 ><br></strong></p>
