DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Calling CCAN DC climate advocates and change-make
 rs: join our ~ spooky ~ DC Activists Meeting on Tuesday\, October 29th from
  6:30 pm to 7:30 pm. </b></strong></p><p>Attend our monthly volunteer meeti
 ng to meet other activists\, hear regular campaign updates\, learn about up
 coming actions\, and take an active role in planning our next steps. </p><p
 >This month\, we will focus on how you can fight Washington Gas’s diabolica
 l Stop Project Pipes plot by  connecting with your ANC or getting involved 
 with yard sign distribution. You will also hear from Meredith about how to 
 get involved with removing eerie invasive vines in DC. </p><p>Meetings are 
 typically held on the last Thursday of the month from 6 pm to 8 pm on Zoom.
  (This month’s meeting has been rescheduled to Tuesday in light of Hallowee
 n!) </p><p><strong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/74575
 /data/1">RSVP now to join the DC activist community!</a></b></strong></p>
