DESCRIPTION:<p>Join us for our crash course on small container gardening th
 at you can do in your own home or apartment. Grow a variety of vegetables a
 nd herbs to give yourself fresh foods that you might not have access to oth
 erwise. During the event we will be giving you your first seeds and portabl
 e containers to begin your garden. This space efficient method for gardenin
 g means you can have fresh produce in any size home! </p><p>This event is t
 he perfect starting point for someone wanting to grow their own food!</p><p
 ><strong><b>WHAT</b></strong>: Grow Your Own Garden: Fight Food Insecurity 
 and Climate Change<br><strong><b>WHEN</b></strong>: Wednesday\, July 17\, 6
 :00 PM ET<br><strong><b>WHERE</b></strong>: Location TBA<br><strong><b>WHAT
  ELSE</b></strong>: Free snacks and drinks will be provided </p><h2><b><str
 ong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/69866/data/1">RSVP t
 oday!</a></b></strong></b></h2><br><b><strong><br></strong></b>
