UID:59rmkfrcbr0drne3ectn68tbdp@google.com
CREATED:20241212T210231Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><b>RSVP</b>: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://a
 ct.ccanactionfund.org/page/77187/data/1&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\
 ;ust=1734469322333008&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0IxJFZ8FNPIlk99vE6Q4oe" target="_blank
 ">https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/77187/data/1</a></p><p><span><b>Descr
 iption</b>: </span><span>Starting on January 8th\, Virginia’s elected offic
 ials will gather in Richmond for the 2025 General Assembly. They will have 
 a short amount of time to pass every single bill they can in 2025.</span></
 p>Those days during session move FAST\, and we need as many people as possi
 ble to make sure our legislators pass bills for clean energy and climate ju
 stice. That&#39\;s why we need YOU.<br><br>Can you join our virtual climate
  champions team? For an hour a week in January and February (or as much tim
 e as you have to give) you can make a BIG difference in passing climate leg
 islation!<br><p>We meet two times a week\, just before important committee 
 hearings for key climate legislation. During the call we explain the key bi
 ll of the day\, and which legislators need to hear from the community. Then
  we give you clear ways to help move that legislator to get the climate bil
 l passed (or the anti-climate bill defeated)! </p><p>Can you help us by sig
 ning up to be a grassroots climate champion for the 2025 General Assembly S
 ession?</p><p>We will meet every Monday from 12:30 - 1:00 pm and every Wedn
 esday from 5:30 - 6:00 pm starting on Monday January 13th and ending Wednes
 day February 19th. </p><p><span>RSVP now!</span></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20241212T210231Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Grassroots Climate Champions - 2025 General Assembly
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
