DESCRIPTION:RSVP: <a href="https://thirdact.org/events/whats-up-docket-key-
 issues-and-topics-on-puc-dockets/?emci=1aea729e-0e07-ef11-96f3-7c1e521b07f9
 &amp\;emdi=ea000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&amp\;ceid=">https://thirdac
 t.org/events/whats-up-docket-key-issues-and-topics-on-puc-dockets/?emci=1ae
 a729e-0e07-ef11-96f3-7c1e521b07f9&amp\;emdi=ea000000-0000-0000-0000-0000000
 00001&amp\;ceid=</a> <br><br>Description: <br><br><br><p>Learn about the en
 ergy justice policies at stake in your state’s Public Utility Commission\, 
 and untangle the spaghetti bowl of insider jargon so you’ll understand how 
 to engage your PUC on your own or with your state Working Group. From Integ
 rated Resource Plans (IRPs) to Power Plant Permits\, from Renewable Energy 
 Portfolio Standards to Rate Cases\, discover how regulators can help change
  our electricity grid from mostly fossil-fueled\, to mostly clean and green
  by 2030.</p><p>Get the big picture on why these dockets are important\, an
 d how Third Actors can make a difference\, pushing for more clean energy\, 
 faster – to stop the build-out of dirty and dangerous fossil gas.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240515T225150Z
