DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Calling all Hampton Roads climate advocates and c
 hange-makers!</b></strong></p><p>CCAN’s 757 Climate Action Team has officia
 lly launched! If you’re looking to take on responsibility and work with a g
 roup of inspiring dedicated climate activists to make a difference in Hampt
 on Roads\, our action team is the right place for you. </p><p>Our next meet
 ing is scheduled for Sunday\, February 16th\, from 1pm-3pm in downtown Norf
 olk. Expect icebreakers\, Valentine’s Day treats\, and real discussions abo
 ut how to make a difference in Hampton Roads climate advocacy. </p><p>This 
 meeting will be hybrid to accommodate members who can't make it in-person\,
  but want to join the meeting online. Snacks and refreshments will be provi
 ded for those who attend in person!</p><p>Don’t miss out—secure your spot t
 oday and be a part of something transformative!</p><h1><b><strong><b><a hre
 f="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/78902/data/1">RSVP today for the 
 location and virtual link!</a></b></strong></b></h1><br><b><strong><br></st
 rong></b>
