UID:2p6iul0g2d99vv1b7urcnfql8p@google.com
CREATED:20231205T162810Z
DESCRIPTION:The Standing Rock Sioux\, Cheyenne River Sioux Tribe\, and gras
 sroots water protectors have led the resistance against the dirty Dakota Ac
 cess Pipeline (DAPL) since the beginning. Now\, thanks to their continued r
 esistance and leadership\, thousands of us have a chance to go on the recor
 d with our support and submit official public comments with the U.S. Army C
 orps of Engineers against this dirty oil pipeline. <strong>Since this is a 
 federal review process\, everyone’s voice matters.</strong><br><br>Together
  we will hear from frontline leaders about the status of the fight\, learn 
 more about how to submit a public comment\, and then have time to write and
  submit our own. <a href="https://url1005.email.actionnetwork.org/ss/c/mRNL
 FKyANPYkYXuUTzk_Sy9FyWzo9kqacbVzd5vG5d2sXsw8BwyDpfxXdrER67jW5-FR9IyDkD8ngeu
 7YROuP-trFi2FhGPPNBvFH5W9gOBFqUDz8tLUNsgTBwDH-OkeoqJFw5VQyMqhY4kvYRAbBCUdVu
 g0pl0-h2qFKgTMIAa86uWTb3xGO23cYxh4dYd75zvMRpESbuyBKjs2oRKeW8FLArs0C0nSDYjCP
 Glr53QZ7DXldQyCdLgtRKwpHCid4KhSHI45kR9x-CJ_lq7vrpGjfszY-t3TYD0smX2D-SPMiyPl
 WEM1eQP8tB7Not8zj_NI4ULd8ljnR9gXnZbAJAww4DAg161i2qZqTpMbPjhYH2NgZBZeQzlyEp1
 cc1I7C3RMxH661b6omgAS6pPozw/41u/nzNU_50jQ7GafeLuI3v1ag/h2/ffM39icx4XS6_uNn3
 jk1vEnYNPXHGiHaGbt81E3d-3I"><strong>REGISTER HERE for the comment party!</s
 trong></a><p><strong></strong></p><p>As frontline Indigenous leaders contin
 ue to show the way\, we must remain steadfast in our support. No longer sho
 uld water\, health\, and life be sacrificed for short-term profits. The Bid
 en administration must side with the people\, not fossil fuel companies\, a
 nd shut down DAPL and fossil fuel infrastructure once and for all. <strong>
 The fossil-free future is here\, if we fight for it.</strong></p><p><strong
 ></strong><strong>P.S. Can’t make it on the 7th?</strong> <a href="https://
 url1005.email.actionnetwork.org/ss/c/CMxF4nARlf6wAFa1PSfv0pxLN8zuXd485gHNRh
 mg2saU56SQzONtsjGKhe1ofZSxABqmn7VGJQJgULdT9Z7aVnOuRDsH1aFYvHH8yfMhJOhiUA8TI
 W_QNvZ9YpPZhADqJb_U4ATjORmrbLw7I5__J76fQGv2bYhmzcaE_2V5oARwcy2tdtb_C02Vkne4
 Y7lqjTw9QtaVgfPBuKykQhzRQd9QfGiVuO1SvctSNqZ85h0P7sl7k-c0kbbZevkbEn7v-YyeaPU
 XuAFlJXipIW4zwTf58H0FG0wU5Cs2ZQJfObjIosecLXfwntPJDtwhYDwaOOiSp7GbspF3Pg1jXy
 3M1EeHAFx94zl9zM26WRa94Z4wA_6LMruwQh3wx7760KyokZhC9ed-Av1wTezFCnN5VQ/41u/nz
 NU_50jQ7GafeLuI3v1ag/h4/gB4zkmglbNqAWI1gPlmfU6TDLiqlk1_YpHkMINqmkao"><stron
 g>Follow the instructions here to submit a comment on your own.</strong></a
 ></p>
