DESCRIPTION:Did you know there's a pipeline fight happening in YOUR backyar
 d!?<p>Washington Gas wants to make ratepayers invest over $4.5 billion into
  rebuilding their methane gas infrastructure in DC — even though we KNOW th
 at methane is making our kids sick\, polluting our air\, and contaminating 
 our green spaces.</p><p>Join us and Extinction Rebellion DC for some free b
 eer and pizza and learn what we're are doing to STOP this pipeline project\
 , and how you can join the fight against this madness!</p><p> RSVP here: <a
  href="https://actionnetwork.org/events/dc-methane-free-happy-hour?source=d
 irect_link&amp\;referrer=group-ccan">https://actionnetwork.org/events/dc-me
