  - <a href="https://ccan.link/2025-PG-Canvasses">RSVP for details</a></span
 ></b></span></span><p><span>We've fought too hard and too long for climate 
 justice in Maryland to stop now. That's why we are not only continuing our 
 work\, we're ramping up our efforts to get even more Marylanders involved —
  and we need YOU! <span>Let's help get the word out about climate justice\,
  including making polluters pay for their contributions to the climate cris
 is and getting toxic gas out of our homes. </span><span><span><span><span><
 span>We'll also ask people to join CCAN!</span></span></span></span></span>
 </span></p><p><span>Building the biggest coalition possible will help make 
 our people-powered climate movement more representative of the diverse comm
 unities in Maryland\, enable us to build powerful volunteer action teams\, 
 and prepare us to have robust in-district meetings with legislators to put 
 pressure on them to support our priority issues. </span></p><h2><span><span
 ><b><span>RSVP today to knock doors or table for climate<br>and environment
 al justice! <a href="https://ccan.link/2025-PG-Canvasses" target="_blank">R
 SVP HERE!</a></span></b></span></span></h2>
