DESCRIPTION:<p><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/70458/dat
 a/1">RSVP FOR ZOOM DETAILS. </a></b></p><p>We are up against a quick deadli
 ne to get all comments in to support stronger regulations for data centers.
 </p><p>Dominion is using data centers to justify expanding fossil fuel infr
 astructure. Our own backyards are being used for these noisy\, polluting be
 hemoths. Data centers are causing Fairfax County to lose traction on its de
 carbonization goals. If we don’t restrict where they can be built\, they wi
 ll also harm its goals for smart growth and transportation\, not to mention
  serious impacts to our communities’ health and ecosystems.</p><p>That’s wh
 ere YOU come in. Join us on Thursday\, July 25 from 12:00-1:00 PM for a vir
 tual comment-writing party on the Data Center Zoning Ordinance Amendment (Z
 OA). Craft an amazing comment that makes a difference!</p><p><strong><b>WHA
 T: </b></strong>Virtual Comment Party to Clean Up Data Centers<br><strong><
 b>WHEN:</b></strong> Thursday\, July 25\, 12:00 PM ET <br><strong><b>WHO:</
 b></strong> This event is co-sponsored by Chesapeake Climate Action Network
 \, Friends of Holmes Run\, Nature Forward\, and Sierra Club Great Falls Gro
 up<br><strong><b>WHERE:</b></strong> Your computer! <a href="https://act.ch
 esapeakeclimate.org/page/70458/data/1">Sign up now for the details</a>. </p
 ><h3><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/70458/data/1">RSVP TOD
 AY!</a></h3>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240719T184919Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Comment Party for Data Centers -- Fairfax County\, VA [virtual even
 t]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
