 ferrer=email_1864100&amp\;email_subject=_announcing-not-on-this-land-the-fi
 ght-against-the-atlantic-coast-pipeline</a><br><br>Description: <span>Appal
 achian Voices and the Southern Environmental Law Center announce an upcomin
 g screening of the documentary film “Not On This Land: The Fight Against th
 e Atlantic Coast Pipeline.”</span><p>Directed by Christopher Landry\, the f
 ilm showcases stories of impacted community members who fought against and 
 helped defeat the fracked-gas Atlantic Coast Pipeline. Hear the incredible 
