 ning at the beautiful Paramount Theater in downtown Charlottesville on Thur
 sday\, April 13 at 7 p.m. After the screening\, organizers will hold a mode
 rated panel discussion about the Atlantic Coast Pipeline\, featuring commun
 ity leaders profiled in the film.</p>
