 4Xd1T5nueOQ_aem_C7kmaFyh_dXEaHHqmfkwIg"><b>RSVP HERE!</b></a><br><br>In a w
 orld where fossil fuels drive health\, environmental\, and economic instabi
 lity\, this event aims to educate and engage artists\, influencers\, and cr
 eatives on how they can be part of the solution. With an emphasis on how th
 e fossil fuel industry harms the environment\, particularly in marginalized
  communities\, we will explore how Black women are leading the charge for s
 ustainable practices in their creativity. The conversation will include way
 s artists can navigate this shifting landscape and make a meaningful impact
  in their work.<br><br>Hosted by the Hip Hop Caucus
