DTEND:20230715T160000Z
DTSTAMP:20260421T015852Z
UID:0avl3j8rh5is7psqtp65n2i154@google.com
CREATED:20230711T170032Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>The Chesapeake Climate Action Network\, Drive Electric Virgi
 nia\, Viridiant\, and Sierra Club invite you to come to our Richmond IRA Ro
 adshow! At the event\, you’ll learn about the Inflation Reduction Act\, and
  how you can utilize it to install sustainable\, electric technologies in y
 our home right now (e.g.\, like solar panels\, a new stove\, or HVAC) with 
 government support.</p><p><b>WHERE</b>: Join us at the Richmond Main Librar
 y Meeting Room (101 E Franklin St\, Richmond\, VA 23219) <br><b>WHEN</b>: S
 aturday\, July 15th from 10:30 - 12:00 PM ET<br></p><p>Here's the schedule:
  </p><ul><li>10:30-10:45am: Food! </li><li>10:45am-11:00: Opening Remarks</
 li><li>11:00 – 11:50am: Electrification Roadshow Workshop<ul><li>What is th
 e Inflation Reduction Act (IRA)?</li><li>IRA Tax Credits and Rebates </li><
 li>IRA for Tax-Exempt Entities  </li><li>Workstation 1: Electric Vehicles w
 ith DVA </li><li>Workstation 2: Home Energy Audit Q&amp\;A with Viridiant</
 li><li>Workstation 3: Home Electrification Improvements </li><li>How do I a
