DESCRIPTION:<p>Chesapeake City Council will be re-voting on the proposed fr
 acked gas compressor station on Tuesday\, July 15\, and we need YOU to show
  up and make your voice heard!</p><p>Here's the plan: </p><ul><li><strong><
 b>Rally Outside City Hall at 5:15 PM: </b></strong>We’ll gather to rally fo
 r clean air and a safe\, sustainable future for Chesapeake. Bring your sign
 s\, your friends\, and your voice!</li><li><strong><b>Pack the Room at 6:30
  PM</b></strong>: Chesapeake City Council will be making a final decision o
 n this dangerous project—and your presence in the room shows that Chesapeak
 e residents are united in opposition. Let’s fill every seat!</li><li><stron
 g><b>Get Your Free Rally Shirt and Snacks!</b></strong> Everyone who attend
 s will receive a FREE rally shirt to wear during the rally and meeting. Sho
 w your support loud and proud! Snack on sweet treats to keep up your energy
 .</li><li><strong><b>Want to Speak at the Meeting?</b></strong> Public comm
 ent is a powerful way to influence Council. If you’d like to speak out agai
 nst the compressor station during the meeting\, we’ll help you prepare your
  remarks and get signed up.<em> Just check the box in the RSVP form to let 
 us know you’re interested in speaking.</em></li></ul><p><b><a href="https:/
 /act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/85448/data/1">RSVP today!</a></b></p><p><br
 ></p>
