DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/6
 1427/data/1">Join our next Virginia Action Member Meetup</a></b></strong></
 p><p><strong><b> to learn how you can effectively advocate for climate poli
 cies during the upcoming General Assembly session!</b></strong></p><p>To wi
 n as many of these legislative fights as possible\, we need you to join us 
 in January to get up to speed on which bills you should be advocating for w
 ith your legislator and which you should be tearing up. As an informed volu
 nteer and constituent\, you hold huge power in swaying your lawmakerand in 
 creating a just\, climate-stable future for all Virginians. </p><p><strong>
 <b>So join us on Monday\, January 8th at 6:30 PM on Zoom to get up to speed
  on all things legislation!</b></strong></p><p>CCAN Action Fund will also p
 rovide updates on our campaigns and more details on how to stay engaged and
  take action throughout the assembly session when we’ll be fighting to make
  climate progress!</p><p><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page
 /61427/data/1">RSVP today!</a></b></p><p><br></p>
