DESCRIPTION:<b><a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/77760/data/1">R
 SVP HERE!</a></b><br><br>On Jan 16th CCAN Action Fund and Sierra Club activ
 ists will travel to Richmond for Grassroots Climate Lobby Day. But before w
 e go\, we need to get prepared! <br><br>If you are coming on the 16th or co
 nsidering joining\, register for this prep call!<br><br>We will go over a r
 eminder on how to lobby and connect you with people in your region to prepa
 re for your meetings and talk logistics. <b><a href="https://act.ccanaction
 fund.org/page/77760/data/1"><u>RSVP today!</u></a></b>
