 ricity costs through the roof! Listen to our expert speakers from across th
 e region speak to what PJM is\, how they're driving our costs up\, and what
  we can do to stop them.</p><p><strong><b>WHAT: </b></strong>Webinar: Why P
 JM is driving up your electricity prices<br><strong><b>WHEN:</b></strong> T
 hursday\, October 9\, 6:00 PM ET<br><strong><b>SPEAKERS: </b></strong>TBA<b
