DESCRIPTION:<p dir="ltr">On Wednesday\, June 5th at 1:00 PM ET\, CCAN is ho
 sting an informational webinar on one of the most important pieces of legis
 lation this Congress will pass: the Farm Bill. <br></p><p dir="ltr">The 202
 3 Farm Bill serves as a major opportunity to confront the agricultural sect
 or's greenhouse gas emissions. This webinar will feature experts who will d
 escribe and explain the Farm Bill's importance\, as well as the process to 
 pass it. We will also discuss ways you can get involved in the effort to pa
 ss a climate-smart Farm Bill.</p><p dir="ltr"><a href="https://act.ccanacti
 onfund.org/page/67660/data/1">Click here to register for the webinar!<br></
 a></p>
