DESCRIPTION:<p>Join us for our next Maryland Legislative Action Meetup!  We
 ’ll update you on our priority climate justice legislation then let you kno
 w how YOU can help pass them. Then we’ll provide storytelling worksheets fo
 r you to craft your own story!</p><p>We’re aiming to pass legislation to in
 crease investments in solar battery storage and in public transit\, as well
  as helping to hold polluters accountable for their contributions to the cl
 imate crisis. But these bills need to pass their chamber of origin in the n
 ext few weeks to have a shot at passing! So sign up today.</p><p><strong><b
 >WHEN</b></strong>:  Thursday\, March 5\, 7:00-8:00 PM ET<br><strong><b>WHE
 RE</b></strong>: Your computer! RSVP for the Zoom info.</p><h3><strong><b><
 a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/94531/data/1">RSVP today!</a></
 b></strong></h3><br><strong><br></strong>
