DESCRIPTION:Description: <span>It is increasingly clear that climate change
  is a calamity not only facing the world at large but </span><span>increasi
 ngly impacting our lives and those of our families. In “Climate Change Conv
 ersations” we </span><span>hope that\, through providing a forum for discus
 sion and learning\, and through the leadership of our </span><span>local mu
 nicipalities and our active co-sponsors\, we will find a way to turn the co
 rner on climate </span><span>change.</span><br><span><br></span>Come and be
  part of the solution: Hear from our featured speakers about innovative eff
 orts already underway and engage with local sponsors about tangible steps y
 ou can take at home\, school\, or in your business.
