DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Calling all Hampton Roads climate advocates and c
 hange-makers!</b></strong></p><p>Our next 757 Climate Action Team meeting i
 s scheduled for <b>Sunday\, December 14th\, from 1:00 - 3:00 PM </b>in-pers
 on or on Zoom. Expect icebreakers\, snacks\, and real discussions about how
  to make a difference in Hampton Roads climate advocacy. </p><p>Our next me
 eting will primarily be focused on the following:</p><ul><li>CCAN's Polar P
 lunge in Virginia Beach</li><li>Lobby training &amp\; Scheduling meetings</
 li><li>Discussing our legislative priorities</li></ul><p>This meeting will 
 be <b>hybrid </b>to accommodate members who are traveling for the holidays!
  I'll be bringing in some holiday treats for those who attend in-person :)<
 /p><p>Don’t miss out—secure your spot today and be a part of something tran
 sformative!</p><p><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/91849/
 data/1">RSVP today!</a></b></p><p><br></p><p>Email <a href="mailto:michelle
 u@chesapeakeclimate.org" target="_blank">michelleu@chesapeakeclimate.org</a
 > with any questions :)</p>
