 ><p>Join author Lawrence MacDonald for a discussion about his new book\, <e
 m>"Am I Too Old to Save the Planet? A Boomer's Guide to Climate Action\," <
 /em>and a conversation between MacDonald and Mike Tidwell\, director and fo
 under of the Chesapeake Climate Action Network. </p><p><strong><b>WHAT</b><
 /strong>: CCAN Presents: Author Talk with Lawrence MacDonald<br><br><strong
 ><b>WHEN</b></strong>: Thursday\, November 2\, 6:00 - 7:30 PM<br><br><stron
 g><b>WHERE</b></strong>: People's Book\,7014 Westmoreland Ave Suite A\, Tak
 oma Park\, MD 20912</p><p><strong><b>AGENDA:</b></strong> </p><ul><li><stro
 ng><b>Author Reading:</b></strong> Lawrence MacDonald will share captivatin
 g excerpts from his latest book</li><li><strong><b>Author Q&amp\;A: </b></s
