  activism\, and the power of individual action</li><li><strong><b>Book Sign
 ing: </b></strong>Get your copy of Am I Too Old to Save the Planet? persona
 lly signed by the author</li><li><strong><b>Conversation </b></strong>with 
 Lawrence MacDonald and Mike Tidwell: Gain unique perspectives as the author
  discusses climate change with me\, the director and founder of CCAN</li><l
 i><strong><b>Light refreshments served</b></strong></li></ul>
