  about how to make a difference in Hampton Roads climate advocacy. </p><p>O
 ur next meeting will primarily be focused on the following:</p><ul><li>Lear
 n more about CCAN’s local campaigns</li><li>Meet other climate activists in
  the area!</li><li>Learn how to remove invasive vines from your local trees
 </li><li>Help plan for our invasive vine removal on March 14th</li><li>Snac
 ks and treats!!</li></ul><p>This meeting will be <strong><b>hybrid </b></st
 rong>to accommodate members who can't make it in-person\, but want to join 
 the meeting online. <em>Snacks and refreshments will be provided for those 
 who attend in person!</em></p><p>Don’t miss out—secure your spot today and 
