 ith from CCAN to remove Invasive Vines at Birchwood at Newton Green senior 
 community in Bladensburg\, MD. <span>We will focus on non-native invasive v
 ines including porcelainberry (Ampelopsis glandulosa var. brevipedunculata)
 \, English ivy (Hedera helix)\, and Kudzu (pueraria montana).</span></p><p>
