DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Join us for a night of virtual action!</b></stron
 g></p><p>Our call will be focused on three things:</p><ol><li>Give you an u
 pdate on where we stand with the RENEW Act veto override and how you can he
 lp. </li><li>Sharing with you how you can get involved in our large scale v
 olunteer program for session\, including joining a lobbying team\, submitti
 ng testimony\, phonebanking\, writing postcards to legislators\, and showin
 g up to rallies and events in Annapolis. </li><li>Teaching how you can be p
 repared to write and submit testimony on the issues you care about. </li></
 ol><p>We are advocating for energy affordability\, making solar accessible 
 to all Marylanders\, investing much more in clean transit\, and advocate fo
 r policies that give our communities a chance to protect ourselves from the
  most devastating consequences of data centers coming to our backyards. </p
 ><p>Join us and be a climate champion for your community this legislative s
 ession. <br><br><strong><b>Sign up now to join us Thursday\, January 8 at 7
 :00 PM!</b></strong></p><p><strong><b><a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.o
 rg/page/91847/data/1" target="_blank">RSVP to get Zoom details! </a></b></s
 trong></p><p><strong><br></strong></p>
