DESCRIPTION:RSVP: <a href="https://www.energyburdencoalition.org/2023-day-o
 f-action">https://www.energyburdencoalition.org/2023-day-of-action</a><br>D
 escription: <span>Join the</span><span> </span><strong>2023 Day of Action f
 or Affordable Energy</strong><span> </span><span>on Thursday\, January 26th
  (8am-12pm) in Richmond\, Virginia. Meeting with your elected officials fac
 e-to-face is the best way to communicate the importance of affordable and c
 lean energy during the Virginia General Assembly legislative session.</span
 ><header><p dir="ltr">Virginia has made incredible progress towards a clean
  energy future\, but the fact is that climate action without consumer prote
 ction is only a job half done. It's time to build on the clean energy progr
 ess we've made with legislation to reign in the costs of our electricity bi
 lls\, prevent utility shutoffs\, and ensure an energy future that works for
  ALL Virginians.</p></header>
