DTSTART:20230509T230000Z
DTEND:20230509T235000Z
DTSTAMP:20260421T015852Z
UID:2fpl2it2tstdpgk57allbilmfj@google.com
CREATED:20230503T183520Z
DESCRIPTION:RSVP: <span> </span><a href="https://naacpva.us/CleanSchoolBus"
 >https://naacpva.us/<wbr />CleanSchoolBus</a><br><br>Description: <span>Rec
 ently\, NAACP launched the Electric School Bus Campaign - let’s do our part
  to make sure it happens in Virginia!</span><br><u></u><br> <br>Black stude
 nts are more likely to have long-term health concerns due to environmental 
 racism. Investments like the funding for the Clean School Bus Program will 
 help to mitigate their exposure. Black and other people of color live in co
 mmunities overburdened with significant levels of toxic greenhouse gas emis
 sions that result from transit sources\, including school bus tailpipe expo
 sure. The Environmental Protection Agency (EPA)\, Clean Bus Program is offe
 ring rebates to replace existing school buses with clean and zero-emission 
 (ZE) buses. The goal is to replace existing outdated school bus fleets with
  clean\, zero emission buses\, to deliver safer\, healthier\, and more envi
 ronmentally sustainable learning environments for children in communities t
 hat have been overburdened by pollution.<u></u><u></u><br> <br>Join us to h
 ear from NAACP representatives\, industry experts\, and community advocates
  to learn what you can to make sure your school district submits its paymen
 t request form and that the funds are distributed equally.  <u></u><u></u>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230503T183520Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY: Transportation Equity In The Commonwealth Series #2: Clean School 
 Bus NAACP Nationwide Campaign [Virtual Partner Event]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20230425T233000Z
DTEND:20230426T002000Z
DTSTAMP:20260421T015852Z
UID:1prdj9tq9b2us4sjdbi25en9p2@google.com
CREATED:20230419T165532Z
DESCRIPTION:RSVP: <a href="https://www.younify.org/sassycivics_4_25?utm_cam
 paign=civics_is_getting_sassy&amp\;utm_medium=email&amp\;utm_source=younifi
 ed">https://www.younify.org/sassycivics_4_25?utm_campaign=civics_is_getting
 _sassy&amp\;utm_medium=email&amp\;utm_source=younified</a><br><br>Descripti
 on: <span>Does working for democracy feel like an uphill battle? Like all y
 our emails and texts and phone calls are just going into a black hole?</spa
 n><br><p>We've got your back. Join us for the first in a three-part trainin
 g series where you'll <strong><b>learn how to shift the balance of power wh
 en it seems impossible.</b></strong></p><p>Register now to:</p><p>1) Learn 
 how uniting with other women can create power.</p><p>2) Understand what you
 r government does and how you can pull the levers to get things done.</p><p
 >3) Get organized and get moving\, whether you're brand new or a seasoned a
 ctivist.</p><p>You don't have to be a fancy lobbyist to make real\, lasting
  change. We've got the tips\, tricks\, and tools that will get you there.</
 p>
