DESCRIPTION:<p>The Southeast Supply Enhancement Project from Transco Willia
 ms is a gigantic fossil fuel expansion proposal that crosses five states. I
 t’s the biggest in the last decade.</p><p>We have to stop it.</p><p><b>RSVP
  HERE: <a href="https://actionnetwork.org/events/virtual-comment-party-stop
 -the-ssep/">https://actionnetwork.org/events/virtual-comment-party-stop-the
 -ssep/</a></b></p><p><br></p><p>Right now federal regulators at the Federal
  Energy Regulatory Commission (FERC) are reviewing Transco’s documents. But
  they’re currently only conducting an “environmental assessment.”</p><p>We 
 are demanding FERC conduct a full “environmental impact statement.” This st
 atement must include the option of not expanding this pipeline.</p><p>We ne
 ed activists like you to submit their comments to FERC. RSVP now for our co
 mment writing party on December 9th at 6:30 PM.</p><p>We will give you ever
 ything you need to know to write an impactful comment against the SSEP.</p>
