 gton-campaign-and-tenants&amp\;email_referrer=email_1986427&amp\;email_subj
 ect=pack-the-arlington-board-meeting-this-saturday-with-the-iceoutofarlingt
 on-campaign-and-tenants&amp\;edit_requested=true</a><br><br>Description: <s
 pan>It's again that time of the month to pack the Arlington Board room. Joi
 n us on Saturday at 8 am for public comments at the Arlington board meeting
 . The #ICEoutofArlington Campaign will speak up at the Arlington board meet
 ing to demand that Arlington county board members remove section 7 of the T
 rust policy and accept a range of identification documents. Community membe
 rs will speak to demand complete protection from Abuse by ICE by ending the
 ir voluntary collaboration and updating the "Trust policy." The #ICEoutofAr
 lington coalition has also sent a</span><span> </span><a href="https://url1
 005.email.actionnetwork.org/ss/c/CMxF4nARlf6wAFa1PSfv0pxLN8zuXd485gHNRhmg2s
 bTRPyp5m-3AFqtVoK05zKiJ2dsJ1qUjLFktLZS5k-aAoPpDofms6DL7vGXGfDsOt0fFvKpI4Lav
 8tvGNG4u_9WufqvF7FFG6pgenqRyWjlkKJSxAJPqxFOka-gzfVjNWNdzhg9IVFWo0tAow1u-EfV
 Cld--t1NO3TUZPBZ9hghexJNQA9beKekfVcrPJcbKa0oRIPAzfifKTMb8IuKXBEn3S6ao9oFXrM
 Y4MuJkmbNGmgUE4R4jmjhEtHxKwUVLINEUzkC7z8S2TWHlHYjiXVJ_fEA77Uqj8k-Y_oMT-VBP6
 ImCOAnzNX6yT9017-vAPMjjDQl1Km3rXajSYjzbGHH-odfho8qTCxpSxPIlp_gATMRWXdevoin0
 mfE_N4TuqeyjnC0GvZvtj8BSfbFbL4VGPfaCK19QPUB72lq5BBbkvWuXkBvBHkGogb6kslOQywt
 6W8elhGyNHavGb4h-Fu-ogWNDjqswSp0hoaQzaqNJA/3xs/dZ48b9YpQBWjavEU3MWC6A/h1/dZ
 fWfuYwIs7DEZFJJL_WdRvNFWzatLTSwlhAGbbfmFE">letter</a><span> </span><span>to
