DESCRIPTION:<h1><strong>Wednesday\, January 8\, 2025 </strong><span>11am – 
 2pm EST</span></h1><p>Register here: <a href="https://www.mobilize.us/ccana
 ctionfund/event/746333/" target="_blank">https://www.mobilize.us/ccanaction
 fund/event/746333/</a></p><p>Join us for our First Day of Session action on
  January 8th at 11 am. We will be gathering at Lawyers Mall to call on the 
 MD legislature to make polluters pay for their contributions to the climate
  crisis (so taxpayers aren't left paying the bill)\, as well as requiring t
 hat all new residential buildings be fully electric\, and getting us on tra
 ck to hit our 100% clean energy take action on climate justice this legisla
 tive session. We need to set the tone for the Maryland General Assembly to 
 ensure they continue to make significant advances to address this climate c
 risis this session.</p><p>Agenda: 11:00 AM - noon: Press conference and ral
 ly 12:00 PM - 2:00 PM: Canvass and lobby legislators as they enter the buil
 ding (We will provide materials and training on site to make sure you are c
 omfortable doing it)</p><p>We look forward to seeing you there!</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20241218T172001Z
