DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><a href="https://actionnetwork.org/events/virtual-ho
 w-to-stop-a-gas-plant-workshop?referrer=group-chesapeake-climate-action-net
 work" target="_blank">RSVP HERE.</a></strong></p><p>Virtual! RSVP at the li
 nk above to receive Zoom info. </p><p>Come learn more about how we can figh
 t back against gas expansion in Virginia! Dominion Energy is planning to bu
 ild six new methane gas fired power plants in Virginia and to dismantle the
  Virginia Clean Economy Act that requires Dominion Energy to phase out foss
 il fuel power plants and reach zero carbon emissions by 2045. Help us defen
 d clean air and a healthy climate and defeat Dominion Energy and other bad 
 actors' plans to expand reliance on gas power plants. <strong><a href="http
 s://actionnetwork.org/events/virtual-how-to-stop-a-gas-plant-workshop?refer
 rer=group-chesapeake-climate-action-network" target="_blank">Say NO to New 
 Gas Plants and YES to Clean\, Renewable Energy!</a></strong> Co-sponsored b
 y CCAN and the No New Gas Plants Coalition.</p>
