DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>CCAN is investing in volunteer leadership teams all 
 across the nation. </strong>Come help us to identify opportunities to take 
 action on critical climate issues in your community. This Power Hour is a g
 reat opportunity to learn how CCAN is building support to address the clima
 te crisis\, how you can get involved\, and what it means to become an Actio
 n Member.<br> </p><p><strong>CCAN is recruiting and developing dozens of vo
 lunteer leaders</strong> who are spearheading public education campaigns to
  stop construction of fossil-fuel pipelines\, build a team of young climate
  champions\, advocate for expanding public transit options\, protect our gr
 een spaces\, and lobby legislators to pass historic legislation\, and more.
  These volunteers have taken on significant leadership roles and have becom
 e critical contributors to the success of our movement<strong>!</strong><br
 > </p><p><strong>Join us for this CCAN Action Member Orientation and see ho
 w you can get more involved.</strong> Thanks for your support. We can't do 
 it without you!</p><p><br></p><p><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org
 /page/63187/data/1">RSVP TODAY!</a></p>
