DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Calling CCAN DC climate advocates and change-make
 rs: join our DC Activists potluck on Wednesday\, December 11 from 6:30 pm t
 o 8:00 pm. </b></strong></p><p>Attend our monthly volunteer meeting to meet
  other volunteers\, hear regular campaign updates\, learn about upcoming ac
 tions\, and take an active role in planning our next steps. This month\, we
  will talk about the timeline and next steps for the Project Pipes campaign
 \, upcoming vine removal events\, and pathways for deeper engagement as vol
 unteers! </p><p>To celebrate the in-person meetup\, we’re having a potluck!
  If you can\, bring a dish! We’ll spend the first half-hour of the event ea
 ting together and getting to know one another. </p><p><strong><b>Who</b></s
 trong>: YOU! <br><strong><b>Where</b></strong>: Community Room at the True 
 Reformer Building: 1200 U Street NW  (a short walk from the U Street/Africa
 n-Amer Civil War Memorial Metro station) <br><strong><b>When</b></strong>: 
 Wednesday\, December 11th from 6:30 pm to 8:00 pm</p><p>This month\, Novemb
 er and December’s meetings are combined because of the busy holiday season.
  Moving forward\, these meetings will be regularly occurring on the last Th
 ursday of the month\, and they will alternate between being held in-person 
 and virtual. </p><p><em>P.S. Message ayla@chesapeakeclimate.org if you have
  any questions or burning ideas for meeting content! </em><br> </p><p><stro
 ng><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/76620/data/1">RSVP no
 w to join the DC activist community!</a></b></strong></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20241202T191729Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:DC Activists Meetup: Potluck Edition [In-Person Event]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
