 tn_savedevents_share_modal&amp\;utm_source=link</a><br><br>Description: <sp
 an>Let's get on an enchanting adventure along the Old Dominion Trail near W
 iehle Reston as we embark on a Fireflies Hike.</span><br><br><p>Our journey
  begins at dusk\, immersing ourselves in the vibrant forest adorned with th
 e flickering lights of fireflies.</p><p>Its a scenic trail\, surrounded by 
 lush greenery and the soothing sounds of nature. We take our time to walk a
 nd talk on this 1 mile hike each way so that we go back to the same spot we
  we started.</p><ul><li>Suitable for all skill levels and ages\, this hike 
 welcomes families\, couples\, and friends alike.</li><li>Remember to wear c
 omfortable walking shoes and bring insect repellent for a delightful outdoo
 r experience.</li></ul><p>Meeting point:<br>Reston North Park and Ride\, 11
 409 Sunset Hills Rd\, Reston\, VA 20190.<br>Walk up to : 1891 Old Reston Av
 e Parking\, Old Reston Avenue\, Reston\, VA<br></p>
