DESCRIPTION:<b>Press Conference Rally on Fairfax County Data Center Expansi
 on</b><br>WHEN: Wednesday\, July 10\; 7 PM<br>WHERE: 6324 Edsall Road\, Ale
 xandria\, VA 22312<br>(near proposed Plaza 500 data center)<br><br>DETAILS:
  Unchecked Data Center Expansion is posing countless threats to Virginia’s 
 water access\, air quality\, energy affordability\, climate progress\, and 
 livable communities. Join us for a rally to call on Fairfax County leaders 
 to set the nationwide standard on protections from data centers. The Fairfa
 x County Board of Supervisors will be holding a key public hearing and anti
 cipated vote on July 16 that will determine the impact of data centers for 
 decades to come. This rally\, just days before the vote\, will call on the 
 county to:<br><br>**Require that data centers be at least 1-mile distance f
 rom a metro station entrance where we need walkable homes and jobs\, not da
 ta centers.<br>**Require that data center be setback 1\,000 feet or more fr
 om residences.<br>**Require that all data centers receive a public hearing 
 and approval through a Special Exception process.<br>**Preserve the applica
 bility language that clearly states the new rules would apply to submitted 
 but not yet approved data center site applications.<br>**Commitment to Imme
 diately Act by the Planning Commission and BOS to address topics not includ
 ed in the Zoning Ordinance amendment\, including: the noise ordinance\, ene
 rgy demand and siting of substations\, and cooling water discharge.<br><br>
 At this rally\, neighbors will demand a policy that protects families from 
 unchecked data center expansion along side fellow Virginians who believe th
 at no data center is worth risking our economic security\, environment\, an
 d future. Communities are asking for a future that puts our health\, econom
 ic security\, and futures before the profits of the data center industry.<b
 r><br>CONTACT: <a target="_blank" href="mailto:Jazmom86@gmail.com">Jazmom86
 @gmail.com</a><br>SPONSOR: Sierra Club Virginia Chapter and Great Falls Gro
 up
LAST-MODIFIED:20240709T204408Z
LOCATION:6324 Edsall Rd\, Alexandria\, VA 22312\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Press Conference Rally on Data Center Expansion [Partner In-Person 
 Event]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
