DESCRIPTION:<span><span><span><span><h2><span><span><b><span>Join us for ou
 r Make Polluters Pay Canvasses in Prince George's County!</span></b></span>
 </span></h2></span></span></span></span><span><span><p><span><span><b><span
 >July 13 from 11:00 AM to 4:00 PM in Clinton - </span></b></span></span><sp
