  target="_blank">RSVP for details</a></span></b></span></span></span></span
 ></p></span></span><span><span><p><span>We've fought too hard and too long 
 for climate justice in Maryland to stop now. That's why we are not only con
 tinuing our work\, we're ramping up our efforts to get even more Marylander
 s involved — and we need YOU! <span>Let's help get the word out about clima
 te justice\, including making polluters pay for their contributions to the 
 climate crisis and getting toxic gas out of our homes. </span><span><span><
 span><span><span>We'll also ask people to join CCAN!</span></span></span></
 span></span></span></p><p><span>Building the biggest coalition possible wil
 l help make our people-powered climate movement more representative of the 
 diverse communities in Maryland\, enable us to build powerful volunteer act
 ion teams\, and prepare us to have robust in-district meetings with legisla
 tors to put pressure on them to support our priority issues. </span></p><h2
 ><span><span><b><span>RSVP today to knock doors or table for climate<br>and
  environmental justice! <a href="https://ccan.link/2025-PG-Canvasses" targe
 t="_blank">RSVP HERE</a>!</span></b></span></span></h2></span></span>
