DESCRIPTION:<p>The fight against dirty and costly data centers has fully ar
 rived in Montgomery County. A company called Atmosphere Data Centers wants 
 to build a 300-megawatt hyperscale data center at the old Dickerson coal pl
 ant site in Montgomery County. The company adamantly refuses to commit to r
 unning that data center on clean energy.</p><p>We need YOUR voice right now
 . Join us for a rally at 11:00 am on Friday March 13th in downtown Silver S
 pring to tell our County Council leaders: “Dirty data centers no! 100% clea
 n power yes!” We’ll be gathering outside the Civic Building in Silver Sprin
 g at Veterans Plaza. All three candidates in the race for County Executive 
 will be attending a town hall that day at noon\, hosted by WAMU radio. So w
 e want to show up outside and be visible with T-shirts and banners\, then a
 ttend the noon town hall.<br></p><p><strong>When</strong>: Friday\, March 1
 3<br></p><ul><li>11:00 AM rally</li><li>12:00 PM town hall</li></ul><p><str
 ong>Where:</strong> Civic Building in Silver Spring at Veterans Plaza\, 1 V
 eterans Pl\, Silver Spring\, MD 20910</p><h3><strong><b><a href="https://ac
 t.ccanactionfund.org/page/94901/data/1" target="_blank">RSVP today!</a></b>
 </strong></h3>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T190927Z
LOCATION:Veterans Plaza\, 1 Veterans Pl\, Silver Spring\, MD 20910\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Say No to Dirty Data Center in Dickerson! Rally for 100% Clean Data
  in Montgomery County
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
