 yToken=mu4BF1u2twAwBOdVMjOQjMGwMGZQtUDX</a><br><br>Description: <span>Hop o
 n board our "Virtual Affordable Housing Bus Tour"\, where we'll bringing th
 e tour to you\, offering an insightful journey into the heart of affordable
  housing initiatives that are transforming communities and changing lives. 
 We're taking you on a virtual ride to showcase a diverse array of affordabl
 e housing in Northern Virginia. Our carefully curated stops include:</span>
 <br>The Waypoint in the City of Alexandria: Let's virtually stroll through 
 Wesley's The Waypoint Apartments in Alexandria\, developed through a partne
 rship with Fairlington Presbyterian Church.<br><br>Groveton Street in Fairf
 ax County: Want to see affordable homeownership in the suburbs? We'll show 
 you around Groveton Street in Fairfax County\, a project led by Habitat of 
 Humanity DC NOVA.<br><br>Loudoun View Senior Residences: Explore living in 
 Loudoun County's APAH and Wellington Development property\, where seniors e
 njoy affordable and dignified living apartments.
