 r for our health and emissions free. We need your help to ensure that Howar
 d County meets its climate goals by passing legislation for “smart from the
  start’ building codes in 2025.  Time to kickoff the Electrify Howard Count
 y 2025 Campaign. Are you in? See you there!</p><p><strong><b>Who: </b></str
 ong>You! And other Howard County Residents </p><p><strong><b>Where: </b></s
 trong>Owen Brown Interfaith Center in Columbia\, 7246 Cradlerock Way Columb
 ia\, MD 21045\, Rm 150</p><p><strong><b>When:</b></strong> October 28\, 7:0
 0pm-8:00pm</p><p><em>Light snacks provided</em><br> </p><h3><strong><b><a h
 ref="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/74570/data/1">RSVP today!</a></b><
 /strong></h3>
