 a> <strong><br></strong><br><strong>Description: </strong><strong>Join us f
 or this CCAN Action Member Orientation and see how you can get more involve
 d.</strong><span> Thanks for your support. We can't do it without you!</spa
 n><br><br><strong>CCAN is investing in volunteer leadership teams all acros
 s Maryland\, Virginia\, Washington DC\, and beyond. </strong>Come help us t
 o identify opportunities to take action on critical climate issues in your 
