 \, CCAN recruited and developed dozens of volunteer leaders</strong> who ar
 e spearheading public education campaigns to stop construction of fossil-fu
 el pipelines\, build a team of young climate champions\, advocate for expan
 ding public transit options\, protect our green spaces\, and lobby legislat
 ors to pass historic wind legislation\, and more. These volunteers have tak
 en on significant leadership roles and have become critical contributors to
  the success of our movement<b>.</b></p>
