DESCRIPTION:<b>RSVP: </b><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/thirdact/event/54
 8101/">https://www.mobilize.us/thirdact/event/548101/</a><br><br><b>Descrip
 tion:</b><br><p>Third Act’s year-long campaign demanding the Big 4 dirty ba
 nks divest from fossil fuels is drawing to a close. Our demands have been m
 et with silence\, so it’s time we take biggeractions to match the gravity o
 f our dire planetary crisis. There’s no time to waste! In the words of the 
 inimitable Bill McKibben\, we must stop burning stuff now\, and Third Act i
 s calling for a <a href="https://thirdact.org/national-day-of-action/">Nati
 onal Day of Action on March 21\, 2023(32123)</a>. </p><p>Washington will be
  one of Third Act’s main events for the National Day of Action\, and Third 
 Actors and their allies are converging in DC on 32123 to expose the unconsc
 ionable acts of these <b>profiteers</b> of fossil fuels and demand divestme
 nt. Vigils begin on 2pm Monday March 20 and the National Day of Action is 3
 -21-23 Tuesday from 10am - 2pm. We invite you to join us for one or both da
 ys! </p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230227T174703Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Third Act Days of Action DC 3-21-23 [Partner Event]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
