DESCRIPTION:Join CCAN as we collect petition signatures to make polluters p
 ay for the climate damage they&#39\;ve caused in DC! <br><br><a href="https
 ://www.google.com/url?q=https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeMXj-ksN5
 ALh1OnEtnwKGe0hK6kTmKyZePBfOoGrEPIGPlVw/viewform?usp%3Ddialog&amp\;sa=D&amp
 \;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1756569186471717&amp\;usg=AOvVaw3CxlyHt8iDtPodqZ
 zjY7lb" target="_blank">RSVP here</a>!<br><br><b>Where:</b> Adams Morgan Da
 y: Unity Park\, 1771 Columbia Rd NW<br><b>When: </b>1pm - 3pm <br><br>Clima
 te change is here\, and DC residents are feeling the impact -through major 
 storms\, flash floods\, and extreme heat. Polluters need to be held account
 able for the cost of these disasters\, which is why CCAN is launching our &
 quot\;Make Polluter Pay&quot\; campaign! <br><br>To prove to Councilmembers
  that DC really cares about this\, we&#39\;ll need to demonstrate that thei
 r constituents care about making polluters pay - that&#39\;s where YOU come
  in. Join us to collect petition signatures and build support in priority d
 istricts. As a special treat\, each volunteer will receive a FREE snack on 
 CCAN! No tabling experience necessary\, we&#39\;ll do a quick training on-s
 ite.
