DESCRIPTION:<p>This year’s election will determine the future of Democracy 
 in America and the global climate. With so much at stake\, we are going to 
 do everything in our power to elect climate champions and defeat climate de
 niers in 2024\, and <strong><b>it’s going to take all of us working togethe
 r to do it. </b></strong></p><p>That’s why we have a plan to mobilize thous
 ands of voters in Pennsylvania\, Maryland and Virginia to show up and vote 
 for a safer climate and a more secure Democracy. On August 1st we will be g
 oing over this election plan in detail and taking action together. Join us!
 </p><p><strong><b>WHAT: </b></strong>Help Elect Climate Champions. Virtual 
 Activist Meeting<br><strong><b>WHEN:</b></strong> Thursday\, August 1\, 7:0
 0 PM ET<br><strong><b>WHERE:</b></strong> Your computer! Zoom info provided
  after you RSVP.</p><p><a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/69865/d
 ata/1">RSVP today!</a></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240708T185000Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Virtual Activist Meeting: Help Elect Climate Champions
TRANSP:OPAQUE
