DESCRIPTION:RSVP: <a href="https://powhr.org/event/powhr-book-club-energy-d
 emocracy/">https://powhr.org/event/powhr-book-club-energy-democracy/</a><br
 ><br>Description: <span>Join POWHR for our 2023 Book Club ‘Cultivating Appa
 lachian Advocates’ series! All those who register can receive a free copy o
 f the book in the mail ahead of the book club\, while supplies last. PLEASE
  fill out your address information if you would like a free copy of the boo
 k!</span><br><p>We will be discussing ‘Energy Democracy: Advancing Equity i
 n Clean Energy Solutions’\, edited by Denise Fairchild and Al Weinrub. Fair
 child and Weinrub created this book “to look critically at how our use of e
 nergy has driven ecosystem destruction\, economic insecurity\, and social i
 njustice… and to promote the new energy paradigm and decentralized energy m
 odel needed for a sustainable future. This is the work of energy democracy.
 ” The title of the book “emphasizes the centrality of racial justice and ec
 onomic justice to an energy democracy movement.”</p><p>Register here: <a hr
 ef="https://us02web.zoom.us/meeting/register/tZcsceCrrzwpHtzPFWCCzoUrfPDZYp
 HP2BXa">https://us02web.zoom.us/meeting/register/tZcsceCrrzwpHtzPFWCCzoUrfP
 DZYpHP2BXa</a></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230126T183752Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:POWHR Book Club: Energy Democracy [Partner Event]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
