 V\, Climate Action Virginia\, Chesapeake Climate Action Network\, Sierra Cl
 ub Virginia Chapter and partners as we rally to defend our climate\, and ce
 lebrate the progress that has benefited the Hampton Roads region so far. In
  August of 2022\, the most historic climate bill was passed and now we must
  work to defend it. With Earth Day just around the corner\, this is the per
 fect opportunity for us to make our voices heard and urge Congress to prote
 ct the national clean energy and climate investments that have already bene
 fited the Hampton Roads region.<br><br>Questions? Email our Federal Campaig
 ns Associate\, Gabby Walton\, at gabby@chesapeakeclimate.org
