DESCRIPTION:<span><span><span><span><span><span><h2><span><span><strong><sp
 an>Join us for our Make Polluters Pay Canvasses in Montgomery County!</span
 ></strong></span></span></h2></span></span></span></span></span></span><spa
 n><span><span><span><p><span><span><strong><span>July 2 from 5:00 PM to 8:0
 0 PM in Aspen Hill - <a href="https://ccan.link/2025-MoCo-Canvasses">RSVP f
 or details</a></span></strong></span></span></p></span></span></span></span
 ><span><span><span><span><p><span>We've fought too hard and too long for cl
 imate justice in Maryland to stop now. That's why we are not only continuin
 g our work\, we're ramping up our efforts to get even more Marylanders invo
 lved — and we need YOU! <span>Let's help get the word out about climate jus
 tice\, including making polluters pay for their contributions to the climat
 e crisis and getting toxic gas out of our homes. </span><span><span><span><
 span><span>We'll also ask people to join CCAN!</span></span></span></span><
 /span></span></p><p><span>Building the biggest coalition possible will help
  make our people-powered climate movement more representative of the divers
 e communities in Maryland\, enable us to build powerful volunteer action te
 ams\, and prepare us to have robust in-district meetings with legislators t
 o put pressure on them to support our priority issues. </span></p><h2><span
 ><span><strong><span>RSVP today to knock doors or table for climate<br>and 
 environmental justice! <a href="https://ccan.link/2025-MoCo-Canvasses">RSVP
  HERE</a>!</span></strong></span></span></h2></span></span></span></span>
