DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Calling all Richmond climate advocates and change
 -makers</b></strong></p><p>CCAN’s Richmond Community Climate Action Team ha
 s officially launched! If you’re looking to take on responsibility and work
  with a group of inspiring dedicated climate activists to make a difference
  in the Richmond area\, our action team is the right place for you. </p><p>
 Our next meeting is scheduled for Wednesday\, January 15th\, from 7pm-8pm i
 n downtown Richmond. Expect icebreakers\, snacks\, and real discussions abo
 ut how to make a difference in Richmond climate advocacy. </p><p>On Wednesd
 ay you can learn more about our team roles\, local campaigns and how you ca
 n get involved.</p><p>This meeting will be hybrid to accommodate members wh
 o can't make it in-person\, but want to join the meeting online. Snacks and
  refreshments will be provided for those who attend in person!</p><p>Don’t 
 miss out—secure your spot today and be a part of something transformative!<
 /p><h1><b><strong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/77809/
 data/1">RSVP today for the location and Zoom info!</a></b></strong></b></h1
 ><br><b><strong><br></strong></b>
