DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>Come to the next virtual CCAN Virginia Action Mem
 ber Meetup. Join us online next Tuesday March 25 at 6:30 PM!</b></strong></
 p><p>Here’s what to expect:</p><ul><li>Organizing updates - From the 757 to
  Chesterfield to NoVA\, volunteers are fighting gas plants\, attending yout
 h environmental conferences and pushing Virginia regulators to plan for a j
 ust climate future.  Ting\, Leianis and Daly will share the latest and how 
 you can get involved!</li><li>Legislative debrief - What climate bills ende
 d up passing? How did your legislator vote? </li><li>Meaningful action - We
  will each write a postcard to our own legislator either thanking them for 
 a good vote or expressing our disappointment on a bad vote. And you can con
 nect with your neighbors to make a plan to meet your legislators in person!
 </li></ul><p>Sending postcards is an effective and quick way to get a perso
 nalized message to your representative. RSVP before March 20 and we will se
 nd you a pre-stamped postcard for you to use during the virtual meeting. </
 p><h1><b><strong><b><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/80162/d
 ata/1">RSVP today for the Zoom info!</a></b></strong></b></h1>
