DESCRIPTION:<p><b><b>Maryland Legislative Priority 2026 Update and How You 
 Can Get Involved!</b></b></p><p>Our focus for this upcoming Maryland legisl
 ative session will be to pass bills that protect money that is set aside fo
 r low-income families to help electrify their homes\, to be dramatically in
 creasing investment in solar\, and to pass balcony solar legislation to mak
 e access to solar ubiquitous and accessible to tenants and condo owners. </
 p><p>In addition to affordability and investments in clean energy\, we want
  to help advocate for clean energy transportation and having more bus route
 s in underserved communities. This means better access to jobs\, healthcare
 \, and educational opportunities and spending a lot less time in traffic. <
 /p><p><strong><b>WHAT: </b></strong>CCAN Action Fund MD Legislative Priorit
 y Preview<br><br><strong><b>WHEN:</b></strong> Thursday\, November 6\, 7:00
 -8:00 PM ET<br><br><strong><b>WHERE:</b></strong> Your computer! Please RSV
 P for Zoom details.</p><h3><a href="https://act.ccanactionfund.org/page/900
 09/data/1">RSVP today!</a></h3>
LAST-MODIFIED:20251029T194115Z
LOCATION:https://us06web.zoom.us/j/88987022427
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:CCAN Action Fund MD Legislative Preview [Virtual Event]
TRANSP:OPAQUE
