 ering on December 13h at 7:00pm</b>! These monthly meetings are a core part
  of our membership structure. This one is special because it’s open to ALL 
 Virginia Ccaners–not just action members.&nbsp\;</p><p><i>Fighting fossil f
 uels: </i>Things are looking bad for Senator Manchin and the Mountain Valle
 y Pipeline\, but our work is not yet done. There is one last chance for the
  Dirty Deal to ride through Congress – so we’ll take some time to catch up 
 AND get to work with some concrete actions this meeting. </p><p><em>Fightin
 g for our communities:&nbsp\;</em>It’s never too early to start lobbying. B
 y joining with other CCANers who are passionate about the climate issues yo
 u care about\, we can have a strong impact in the upcoming general assembly
  session.&nbsp\;</p><p><strong><b>WHO</b></strong>: Virginians across the C
 ommonwealth\, CCAN’s dedicated organizers\, and you!&nbsp\;<br><br><strong>
 <b>WHAT</b></strong>: Fight against the MVP and for climate justice.&nbsp\;
 This is a special limited-edition of our CCAN Virginia Action Member Meetup
 .<br><br><strong><b>WHERE</b></strong>: On Zoom! RSVP to get the Zoom detai
 ls.&nbsp\;<br><br><strong><b>WHEN</b></strong>: Tuesday\, December 13\, 7:0
 0 PM&nbsp\;</p>
