CREATED:20250510T030216Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/85129/data/1
 "><strong><b>Join us for August 2025 </b></strong><strong><b>CCAN Power Hou
 r - FREE! </b></strong></a></p><p><br></p><p>CCAN is building communities o
 f people who want to help fight climate change and to advance climate\, ene
 rgy\, and environmental justice issues  across the Maryland\, Virginia\, Wa
 shington DC region and beyond.</p><p>The Power Hour is our new member orien
 tation! It’s free\, virtual and a great chance to make a new friend.</p><p>
 Join us for our Power Hour to learn about CCAN\, the amazing work our volun
 teers have done\, our ongoing CCAN projects and campaigns\, and meet some w
 onderful like-minded people. With the ongoing attacks on our climate (like 
 Trump's anti-climate budget bill) politics can feel overwhelming. The const
 ant reminder of the scale of the challenge and its impact on our communitie
 s  like the horrible Texas flood can sometimes make people throw their hand
 s up and say\, well the climate crisis is already here. But\, together\, we
  can help each other fight back in ways that are meaningful and strategic. 
 </p><p><a href="https://act.chesapeakeclimate.org/page/85129/data/1"><b>SIG
 N UP for Action Member Orientation\, 7 PM-8 PM ET on Tuesday\, August 19th\
 , 2025</b></a></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250915T134245Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Power Hour: New Member Orientation
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
