DESCRIPTION:<p>This Sunday\, September 29th at 11am in Norfolk\, all CCAN H
 ampton Roads volunteers are invited to join the <strong><b><strong><b>UVA C
 lub of Tidewater </b></strong></b></strong>for a Cavaliers Care volunteer o
 pportunity! We&#39\;ll be joining <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=htt
 ps://theboldmariner.com/pages/beach-clean-up&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar
 &amp\;ust=1727562498456826&amp\;usg=AOvVaw2yfaEejwm91ufXSHd39VWo" target="_
 blank"><u>Bold Mariner&#39\;s Monthly Beach Cleanup</u></a>. <br></p><p>Sup
 plies (gloves\, bags\, grabbers\, sanitizer) will be provided by Keep Norfo
 lk Beautiful\, but feel free to bring your own if you prefer. After the cle
 anup (which will last about an hour or so)\, we&#39\;ll be back at Bold Mar
 iner for a complimentary drink and socialize.</p><p><b>We will meet at Bold
  Mariner at 10:50 a.m. and walk to the beach as a group by 11</b>. This is 
 a family and dog-friendly event.</p><p>RSVP today! <a href="https://www.goo
 gle.com/url?q=https://www.eventbrite.com/e/uva-club-of-tidewater-cavs-care-
 beach-cleanup-with-bold-mariner-registration-989026152847?aff%3Doddtdtcreat
 or&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1727562498456826&amp\;usg=AOvVaw
 1YI3sxzZbxHTBGXWSqyklG" target="_blank">https://www.eventbrite.com/e/uva-cl
 ub-of-tidewater-cavs-care-beach-cleanup-with-bold-mariner-registration-9890
 26152847?aff=oddtdtcreator</a></p><p>If you have any questions regarding th
 is event\, please contact Leianis Gunn\, Hampton Roads Organizer\, at <a hr
 ef="mailto:leianis@chesapeakeclimate.org" target="_blank">leianis@chesapeak
 eclimate.org</a>.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240923T222903Z
