 lcoming-fireflies-and-other-creatures-to-your-yard/">https://mgnv.org/event
 /the-hospitable-gardener-welcoming-fireflies-and-other-creatures-to-your-ya
 rd/</a><br><br>Description: <span>Are you charmed on summer evenings by the
  tiny bobbing lights of amorous fireflies? Many non-human creatures share t
 he property we call our own\, and we can improve the quality of their lives
  and support the environment by the way we garden. This talk by Extension M
 aster Gardener and Master Naturalist</span><span> </span><strong><b>Alyssa 
 Ford Morel</b></strong><span> </span><span>looks at fireflies\, hummingbird
 s\, lady bugs\, and other creatures with whom we share our yards\, and sugg
 ests practices to welcome and support them. You will learn ways to start ad
 dressing the biodiversity crisis at home.</span>
